  <head>
    <title>设计前期场地与建筑设计（知识）第六章 城市规划基础知识</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <outline text="设计前期场地与建筑设计（知识）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%88%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第六章   城市规划基础知识" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD%E7%AB%A0%20%20%20%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第一节   城市与城市规划理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="一、城市的形成" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）城市的形成" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="随着人类生产的发展，农业从畜牧业中分离，产生了固定的居民点。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E4%BB%8E%E7%95%9C%E7%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%88%86%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%86%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%82%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="由于生产力的提高，产生了以物易物的生产品交换，也就是我国古代《易经》所说的“日中为市，致天下之民，聚天下之货，交易而退，各得其所”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%8A%9B%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%86%E4%BB%A5%E7%89%A9%E6%98%93%E7%89%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E3%80%8A%E6%98%93%E7%BB%8F%E3%80%8B%E6%89%80%E8%AF%B4%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%BA%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%B4%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E4%B9%8B%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%8C%E8%81%9A%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E4%B9%8B%E8%B4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E8%80%8C%E9%80%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%84%E5%BE%97%E5%85%B6%E6%89%80%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="随着交换频繁，逐渐出现了专门从事交易的商人，交易场所也由临时的改为固定的市。由于生活需要的多样化，劳动分工的加强，出现了专门的手工业者。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A2%E9%A2%91%E7%B9%81%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%93%E9%97%A8%E4%BB%8E%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E7%9A%84%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E4%B9%9F%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%B4%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%BA%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E6%A0%B7%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%93%E9%97%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E8%80%85%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="商业与手工业从农业中分离出来，些具有商业及手工业职能的居民点就形成了城市。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%8E%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E4%BB%8E%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%88%86%E7%A6%BB%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%9B%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E5%8F%8A%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E8%81%8C%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%82%B9%E5%B0%B1%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="可以说城市是生产发展和人类第二次劳动大分工的产物。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AF%B4%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E7%89%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="据考证，人类历史上最早的城市出现在公元前3000年左右。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8D%AE%E8%80%83%E8%AF%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D3000%E5%B9%B4%E5%B7%A6%E5%8F%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="中国春秋战国时期，在《墨子》文献中，记载有关于城市建设与攻防战术的内容，各诸侯国之间攻伐频繁，也正是在这个时期，形成了中国古代历史上一个筑城的高潮。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%A2%A8%E5%AD%90%E3%80%8B%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%8E%E6%94%BB%E9%98%B2%E6%88%98%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%84%E8%AF%B8%E4%BE%AF%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E6%94%BB%E4%BC%90%E9%A2%91%E7%B9%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E6%AD%A3%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%AD%91%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E6%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="农业社会时代的城市称为古代城市，工业化时代的城市称为近代城市。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%96%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E8%BF%91%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）城市的含义" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="古代城市，城是一种防御的构筑物，市是交易场所。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E9%98%B2%E5%BE%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="现代城市，包含人口数量产业结构及社会行政三层意义的聚居地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%82%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E8%81%9A%E5%B1%85%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市定义：城市是一定社会的物质空间形态，其人口具有一定规模，其居民大多数从事非农业生产活动的聚居地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%E4%BB%8E%E4%BA%8B%E9%9D%9E%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%81%9A%E5%B1%85%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）城市的特征" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）城市是一定地域的政治、经济、文化中心。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）城市是人类物质文明和精神文明发展的产物，是历史文化的积淀。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E5%92%8C%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E7%89%A9%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%AF%E6%B7%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）城市是一个社会化、多功能、有机的整体，是一个复杂的、动态的综合体。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E5%A4%9A%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%80%81%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%9A%84%E3%80%81%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E4%BD%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市的产生、发展和建设，受社会、经济、文化科学技术及地理环境等多种因素影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%97%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%8F%8A%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市是由于人类在聚居中对防御、生产、生活等方面的要求而产生，并随着这些要求的变化而发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E5%9C%A8%E8%81%9A%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%AD%E5%AF%B9%E9%98%B2%E5%BE%A1%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%80%8C%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E8%80%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="人类聚居形成社会，城市建设要适应和满足社会的需求，同时也受到科学技术发展的促进和制约。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E8%81%9A%E5%B1%85%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A6%81%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E5%92%8C%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%97%E5%88%B0%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%83%E8%BF%9B%E5%92%8C%E5%88%B6%E7%BA%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="二、城市规划学科的发展" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市规划是为了合理地制定城市规模和发展方向，实现城市的经济和社会发展目标，对城市物质空间建设及其时间顺序安排的综合部署。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="其目的是为城市社会的生存和发展立一个良好时空秩序，以满足市民的物质文明和精神文明日益发展的需要。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%AB%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E6%97%B6%E7%A9%BA%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E5%92%8C%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%8A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="城市规划涉及政治、经济、文化、科学技术、建筑、地理、历史、资源、环境、美学、艺术等方面内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E3%80%81%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E3%80%81%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市规划是一门综合学科。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E9%97%A8%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市规划理论是随着人类社会的不断发展而发展的，因此，城市规划是一门动态的、发展中的学科。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E6%98%AF%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%80%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E9%97%A8%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E7%9A%84%E3%80%81%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）古代的城市规划理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.中国古代城市规划的概况" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%86%B5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="中国古代，关于城镇修建、房屋建造的论述多是以阴阳、五行、堪舆学的方式出现，许多理论和学说散见于《周礼》、《商君书》、《管子》和《墨子》等政治、伦理、经史书中。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%81%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BA%E8%BF%B0%E5%A4%9A%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E9%98%B4%E9%98%B3%E3%80%81%E4%BA%94%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%81%E5%A0%AA%E8%88%86%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%B8%E5%A4%9A%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E5%92%8C%E5%AD%A6%E8%AF%B4%E6%95%A3%E8%A7%81%E4%BA%8E%E3%80%8A%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%E3%80%8B%E3%80%81%E3%80%8A%E5%95%86%E5%90%9B%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%8B%E3%80%81%E3%80%8A%E7%AE%A1%E5%AD%90%E3%80%8B%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8A%E5%A2%A8%E5%AD%90%E3%80%8B%E7%AD%89%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%81%E4%BC%A6%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E5%8F%B2%E4%B9%A6%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="中国奴隶社会的城市是在奴隶主封地中心（邑）的基础上发展起来的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%A5%B4%E9%9A%B6%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8%E5%A5%B4%E9%9A%B6%E4%B8%BB%E5%B0%81%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%88%E9%82%91%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="商代开始出现了我国的城市雏形，如：商代早期建设的河南偃师商城，中期建设的位于今天郑州的商城、安阳的殷墟和位于今天湖北的盘龙城。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%95%86%E4%BB%A3%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%9B%8F%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%EF%BC%9A%E5%95%86%E4%BB%A3%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%B3%E5%8D%97%E5%81%83%E5%B8%88%E5%95%86%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E9%83%91%E5%B7%9E%E7%9A%84%E5%95%86%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E9%98%B3%E7%9A%84%E6%AE%B7%E5%A2%9F%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%98%E9%BE%99%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="周代召公和周公曾去相土勘测定址，进行了有目的、有计划、有步骤的城市建设，这是中国历史上第一次有明确记载的城市规划事件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%91%A8%E4%BB%A3%E5%8F%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%92%8C%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AC%E6%9B%BE%E5%8E%BB%E7%9B%B8%E5%9C%9F%E5%8B%98%E6%B5%8B%E5%AE%9A%E5%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%86%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E3%80%81%E6%9C%89%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E6%9C%89%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E8%AE%B0%E8%BD%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="成书于春秋战国之际的《周礼·考工记》记述了周代王城建设的空间布局：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%90%E4%B9%A6%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E9%99%85%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8A%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%C2%B7%E8%80%83%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%B0%E3%80%8B%E8%AE%B0%E8%BF%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%91%A8%E4%BB%A3%E7%8E%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="“匠人营国，方九里，旁三门。国中九经九纬，经涂九轨。左祖右社，面朝后市。市朝一夫。”" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E5%8C%A0%E4%BA%BA%E8%90%A5%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%B9%E4%B9%9D%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%81%E4%B8%89%E9%97%A8%E3%80%82%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%AD%E4%B9%9D%E7%BB%8F%E4%B9%9D%E7%BA%AC%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B6%82%E4%B9%9D%E8%BD%A8%E3%80%82%E5%B7%A6%E7%A5%96%E5%8F%B3%E7%A4%BE%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%A2%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%9D%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%AB%E3%80%82%E2%80%9D%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="书中还记述了按照封建等级，不同级别的城市建设形制，如“都”、“王城”和“诸侯城”等都规定城市用地面积、道路宽度、城门数目、城墙高度等方面的等级差别；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B9%A6%E4%B8%AD%E8%BF%98%E8%AE%B0%E8%BF%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E5%B0%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%BD%A2%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E2%80%9C%E9%83%BD%E2%80%9D%E3%80%81%E2%80%9C%E7%8E%8B%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%9D%E5%92%8C%E2%80%9C%E8%AF%B8%E4%BE%AF%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%9D%E7%AD%89%E9%83%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E3%80%81%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E9%97%A8%E6%95%B0%E7%9B%AE%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%A2%99%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E5%B7%AE%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="同时还有城外的郊、田、林、牧地的相关论述，强调整体观念和长远发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E9%83%8A%E3%80%81%E7%94%B0%E3%80%81%E6%9E%97%E3%80%81%E7%89%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E8%AE%BA%E8%BF%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%B5%E5%92%8C%E9%95%BF%E8%BF%9C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
        <outline text="《周礼考工记》记述的周代城市建设的空间布局的形制，对中国古代城市规划实践活动产生了深远的影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%E8%80%83%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%B0%E3%80%8B%E8%AE%B0%E8%BF%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%91%A8%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%86%E6%B7%B1%E8%BF%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
          <outline text="如隋唐时代由宇文恺创建的长安城，元代刘秉忠规划的元大都等城市，其布局严整、分区明确，以宫城为中心，道路、街坊、市肆的位置以中轴线对称布置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E9%9A%8B%E5%94%90%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%B1%E5%AE%87%E6%96%87%E6%81%BA%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E5%88%98%E7%A7%89%E5%BF%A0%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E7%AD%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%A5%E6%95%B4%E3%80%81%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%AB%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E3%80%81%E5%B8%82%E8%82%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
          <outline text="从秦汉到明清，中国历代城市规划思想，反映了中国古代宗法礼制文化、体现了以儒家为代表的维护礼制、皇权至上的理念（图6-1）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%8E%E7%A7%A6%E6%B1%89%E5%88%B0%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8E%86%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%A4%BC%E5%88%B6%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E4%BB%A5%E5%84%92%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%A4%BC%E5%88%B6%E3%80%81%E7%9A%87%E6%9D%83%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE6-1%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        </outline>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="战国时代的城市布局，丰富了城市规划理念，伍子胥提出了“相土尝水，象天法地”的规划思想。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E4%BA%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%8D%E5%AD%90%E8%83%A5%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E7%9B%B8%E5%9C%9F%E5%B0%9D%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%8C%E8%B1%A1%E5%A4%A9%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%B0%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="他主持规划建造了吴国国都阖闾城，充分考虑了江南水乡的特点一—水网、交通、排水布局——展示了水乡城市规划的高超技巧。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%96%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E4%BA%86%E5%90%B4%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E9%83%BD%E9%98%96%E9%97%BE%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E4%BA%86%E6%B1%9F%E5%8D%97%E6%B0%B4%E4%B9%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E4%B8%80%E2%80%94%E6%B0%B4%E7%BD%91%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E3%80%81%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%B0%B4%E4%B9%A1%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E8%B6%85%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="越国的范蠡按照《孙子兵法》为国都选址。临淄城的规划则因地制宜，根据自然地形布局，南北向取直，东西向沿河曲折，防洪排涝设施精巧实用，并与防御功能完美结合。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%B6%8A%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%8C%83%E8%A0%A1%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E3%80%8A%E5%AD%99%E5%AD%90%E5%85%B5%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%BA%E5%9B%BD%E9%83%BD%E9%80%89%E5%9D%80%E3%80%82%E4%B8%B4%E6%B7%84%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%88%99%E5%9B%A0%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9C%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E5%90%91%E5%8F%96%E7%9B%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%E5%90%91%E6%B2%BF%E6%B2%B3%E6%9B%B2%E6%8A%98%EF%BC%8C%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E6%8E%92%E6%B6%9D%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%B2%BE%E5%B7%A7%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8E%E9%98%B2%E5%BE%A1%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="鲁国济南城也打破严格对称格局，与水体和谐布置。赵国的国都建设考虑北方特点，高台建设，壮丽的视觉效果与城市防御功能相得益彰。而江南淹国国都淹城，城与河浑然一体，自然蜿蜒，利于防御。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%B2%81%E5%9B%BD%E6%B5%8E%E5%8D%97%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%9F%E6%89%93%E7%A0%B4%E4%B8%A5%E6%A0%BC%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E6%A0%BC%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E6%B0%B4%E4%BD%93%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%E8%B5%B5%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BD%E9%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%B0%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%A3%AE%E4%B8%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%98%B2%E5%BE%A1%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%B8%E5%BE%97%E7%9B%8A%E5%BD%B0%E3%80%82%E8%80%8C%E6%B1%9F%E5%8D%97%E6%B7%B9%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E9%83%BD%E6%B7%B9%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%8E%E6%B2%B3%E6%B5%91%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%93%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E8%9C%BF%E8%9C%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E9%98%B2%E5%BE%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="《管子》立正篇：“凡立国都，非于大山之下，必于广川之上。高毋近旱而水用足，下毋近水而沟防省。因天材，就地利，故城郭不必中规矩，道路不必中准绳。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E7%AE%A1%E5%AD%90%E3%80%8B%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A3%E7%AF%87%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E5%87%A1%E7%AB%8B%E5%9B%BD%E9%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%9E%E4%BA%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%B1%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%85%E4%BA%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%B7%9D%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%82%E9%AB%98%E6%AF%8B%E8%BF%91%E6%97%B1%E8%80%8C%E6%B0%B4%E7%94%A8%E8%B6%B3%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E6%AF%8B%E8%BF%91%E6%B0%B4%E8%80%8C%E6%B2%9F%E9%98%B2%E7%9C%81%E3%80%82%E5%9B%A0%E5%A4%A9%E6%9D%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%85%E5%9F%8E%E9%83%AD%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%85%E4%B8%AD%E8%A7%84%E7%9F%A9%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%85%E4%B8%AD%E5%87%86%E7%BB%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="”从思想上打破了《周礼》单一模式的束缚，强调了人工环境与自然环境的和谐。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%E4%BB%8E%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%93%E7%A0%B4%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8A%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%E3%80%8B%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%9F%E7%BC%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E4%BA%86%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="《商君书》则更多地从城乡关系、区域经济和交通布局的角度，对城市的发展和城市的管理制度进行了阐述。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%95%86%E5%90%9B%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%8B%E5%88%99%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%B0%E4%BB%8E%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%86%E9%98%90%E8%BF%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="秦统一中国后，发展了“象天法地”的理念，即强调方位，以天体星象坐标为依据，布局灵活具体。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A7%A6%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E8%B1%A1%E5%A4%A9%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%B0%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E6%96%B9%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%93%E6%98%9F%E8%B1%A1%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E4%B8%BA%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="西汉国都长安的城市布局并不规则（见图4-8），没有贯穿全城的对称轴线，说明周礼制布局没有得到实现。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E6%B1%89%E5%9B%BD%E9%83%BD%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99%EF%BC%88%E8%A7%81%E5%9B%BE4-8%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E8%B4%AF%E7%A9%BF%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%E5%88%B6%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="东汉洛邑城（即今之洛阳）空间规划布局为长方形，整个城市的南北轴线上分布了宫殿，强调了皇权，周礼制的规划思想理念得到全面的体现。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%9C%E6%B1%89%E6%B4%9B%E9%82%91%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%88%E5%8D%B3%E4%BB%8A%E4%B9%8B%E6%B4%9B%E9%98%B3%EF%BC%89%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%BA%E9%95%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%BD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8A%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E4%BA%86%E5%AE%AB%E6%AE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E4%BA%86%E7%9A%87%E6%9D%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="三国时期，魏王邺城规划继承了战国时期以宫城为中心的规划思想，功能分区明确、结构严谨，城市交通干道轴线与城门对齐，道路分级明确（见图4-9）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E9%AD%8F%E7%8E%8B%E9%82%BA%E5%9F%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF%E4%BA%86%E6%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%AB%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E3%80%81%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%A5%E8%B0%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%93%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E9%97%A8%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%88%86%E7%BA%A7%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%EF%BC%88%E8%A7%81%E5%9B%BE4-9%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="邺城的规划布局对以后的中国古代城市规划思想的发展产生了重要影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%82%BA%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%AF%B9%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%86%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="吴国国都迁都于金陵，其城市用地依自然地势发展，以石头山、长江险要为界，皇宫位于城市南北中轴线上，重要建筑以此对称布局。金陵是周礼制城市规划思想和与自然结合的规划理念相结合的典范。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%B4%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E9%83%BD%E8%BF%81%E9%83%BD%E4%BA%8E%E9%87%91%E9%99%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%BE%9D%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%BF%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E7%9F%B3%E5%A4%B4%E5%B1%B1%E3%80%81%E9%95%BF%E6%B1%9F%E9%99%A9%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%BA%E7%95%8C%EF%BC%8C%E7%9A%87%E5%AE%AB%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%A4%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%E9%87%91%E9%99%B5%E6%98%AF%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%E5%88%B6%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%E7%9B%B8%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B8%E8%8C%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="公元7世纪，由宇文恺规划建造的隋唐长安城，整个城市布局严整，分区明确，以宫城为中心，“官民不相参”（见图4-2）。城市道路系统、坊里、市肆的位置以中轴线对称布局。里坊制在唐长安得到进一步发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%837%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E5%AE%87%E6%96%87%E6%81%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%8B%E5%94%90%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%A5%E6%95%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%AB%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%8C%E2%80%9C%E5%AE%98%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%8D%E7%9B%B8%E5%8F%82%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88%E8%A7%81%E5%9B%BE4-2%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%81%E5%9D%8A%E9%87%8C%E3%80%81%E5%B8%82%E8%82%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%E9%87%8C%E5%9D%8A%E5%88%B6%E5%9C%A8%E5%94%90%E9%95%BF%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="五代后周世宗柴荣在显德二年，为改、扩建东京（汴梁）而发布的诏书，论述了城市改建和扩建要解决的问题，是中国古代关于城市建设的一份杰出文件，为研究中国古代“城市规划和管理问题”提供了代表性文献。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%A3%E5%90%8E%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%96%E5%AE%97%E6%9F%B4%E8%8D%A3%E5%9C%A8%E6%98%BE%E5%BE%B7%E4%BA%8C%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E6%94%B9%E3%80%81%E6%89%A9%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%AC%EF%BC%88%E6%B1%B4%E6%A2%81%EF%BC%89%E8%80%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%8F%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%BA%E8%BF%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%94%B9%E5%BB%BA%E5%92%8C%E6%89%A9%E5%BB%BA%E8%A6%81%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%BD%E6%9D%B0%E5%87%BA%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E2%80%9C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E2%80%9D%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%BA%86%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%80%A7%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="宋代开封城按此诏书进行了有规划的城市扩建。随着商品经济的发展，在开封城中开始出现了开放的街巷制，延续数千年的里坊制度逐渐被废除，这是中国古代城市规划思想的重要发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%8B%E4%BB%A3%E5%BC%80%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E6%8C%89%E6%AD%A4%E8%AF%8F%E4%B9%A6%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%86%E6%9C%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%89%A9%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%82%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%97%E5%B7%B7%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%B6%E7%BB%AD%E6%95%B0%E5%8D%83%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8C%E5%9D%8A%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E8%A2%AB%E5%BA%9F%E9%99%A4%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="元代由刘秉忠规划建设的元大都（见图4-6），明清时代在元大都基础上建造的北京城（见图4-4、图4-5），都是根据当时的政治、经济、文化发展的需求，结合了当地的地形地貌特点，按照《周礼·考工记》所述的王城空间布局制度而规划建设的都城。整个城市以宫城为中心，功能分区明确，布局严整，道路、街坊、市肆以南北中轴线对称布置，充分体现了皇权至上和封建社会的等级秩序；城市住宅院落、大型公共建筑的组合、形式、规模、色彩，也都主次尊卑等级分明，中轴对称。这是中国封建社会后期的都城代表，充分表明中国儒家思想对中国古代城市规划思想的深刻影响，反映了中国古代宗法礼制的文化理念和“天人合一”的中国古代哲学思想。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%83%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%B1%E5%88%98%E7%A7%89%E5%BF%A0%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%EF%BC%88%E8%A7%81%E5%9B%BE4-6%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%88%E8%A7%81%E5%9B%BE4-4%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BE4-5%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E4%BA%86%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E5%9C%B0%E8%B2%8C%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E3%80%8A%E5%91%A8%E7%A4%BC%C2%B7%E8%80%83%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%B0%E3%80%8B%E6%89%80%E8%BF%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%8B%E5%9F%8E%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E8%80%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%82%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%AB%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%A5%E6%95%B4%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E3%80%81%E5%B8%82%E8%82%86%E4%BB%A5%E5%8D%97%E5%8C%97%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E7%BA%BF%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E7%9A%87%E6%9D%83%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8A%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F%EF%BC%9B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E3%80%81%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%A1%E5%B0%8A%E5%8D%91%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%86%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%B4%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%82%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%90%8E%E6%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%84%92%E5%AE%B6%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B1%E5%88%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%A4%BC%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%E5%92%8C%E2%80%9C%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%88%E4%B8%80%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%A6%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.西方古代城市规划概况" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%A6%82%E5%86%B5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="西方古代，公元前500年的古希腊城邦时期，在城市建设中有希波丹姆模式，提出了方格形的道路系统和广场设在城中心等建设原则。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D500%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A4%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%E5%9F%8E%E9%82%A6%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%8C%E6%B3%A2%E4%B8%B9%E5%A7%86%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%96%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%BD%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%AD%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="此模式，在米列都城和提姆加得城得到完整体现（图6-2、图6-3）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E7%B1%B3%E5%88%97%E9%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%92%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%A7%86%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%97%E5%9F%8E%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE6-2%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BE6-3%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="以城市广场为中心，反映了古希腊的市民民主文化。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%A5%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E4%BA%86%E5%8F%A4%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="公元前1世纪，古罗马建筑师维特鲁威的著作《建筑十书》，是西方古代最完整的古典建筑典籍，内有城市规划的论述。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%83%E5%89%8D1%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%A4%E7%BD%97%E9%A9%AC%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E7%BB%B4%E7%89%B9%E9%B2%81%E5%A8%81%E7%9A%84%E8%91%97%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8D%81%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%8F%A4%E4%BB%A3%E6%9C%80%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%A4%E5%85%B8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%85%B8%E7%B1%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BA%E8%BF%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="欧洲中世纪城市多为自发成长。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%8F%91%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1889年，维也纳建筑师卡美洛西特出版的《按照艺术原则进行城市设计》一书，对欧洲中世纪城市进行描述，这是一本较早的城市设计论著。它力争从城市美学和艺术角度解决大城市的环境和社会问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1889%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%B4%E4%B9%9F%E7%BA%B3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%8D%A1%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%9B%E8%A5%BF%E7%89%B9%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8A%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%AC%E8%BE%83%E6%97%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AE%BA%E8%91%97%E3%80%82%E5%AE%83%E5%8A%9B%E4%BA%89%E4%BB%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E5%92%8C%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）近现代城市规划理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E8%BF%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在工业革命之后，城市急剧膨胀，城市矛盾日益尖锐。如居住拥挤、环境恶化、交通堵塞等问题，直接危害人民生活和社会发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A5%E5%89%A7%E8%86%A8%E8%83%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%8A%E5%B0%96%E9%94%90%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E6%8B%A5%E6%8C%A4%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%81%B6%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%A0%B5%E5%A1%9E%E7%AD%89%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="为解决这些矛盾，在欧美先后提出了种种城市规划思想、理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E6%AC%A7%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%88%E5%90%8E%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E7%A7%8D%E7%A7%8D%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E3%80%81%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.空想社会主义的城市与“田园城市”理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E7%A9%BA%E6%83%B3%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8E%E2%80%9C%E7%94%B0%E5%9B%AD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E2%80%9D%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="空想社会主义的城市规划理论是针对资本主义城市的城乡对立而提出的改革方案。其中有：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A9%BA%E6%83%B3%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E6%98%AF%E9%92%88%E5%AF%B9%E8%B5%84%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E5%AF%B9%E7%AB%8B%E8%80%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%82%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）托马斯·摩尔（Thomas More）在16世纪提出的“乌托邦”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%89%98%E9%A9%AC%E6%96%AF%C2%B7%E6%91%A9%E5%B0%94%EF%BC%88Thomas%20More%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A816%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E4%B9%8C%E6%89%98%E9%82%A6%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）康帕内拉（Tommaso Campanelta）1602年的著作《太阳城》。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%BA%B7%E5%B8%95%E5%86%85%E6%8B%89%EF%BC%88Tommaso%20Campanelta%EF%BC%891602%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%91%97%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%8A%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）傅立叶（Charles Fourier）以名为“法郎吉”（Phalange）生产者联合会为单位的组织社会化大生产等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%82%85%E7%AB%8B%E5%8F%B6%EF%BC%88Charles%20Fourier%EF%BC%89%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E6%B3%95%E9%83%8E%E5%90%89%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88Phalange%EF%BC%89%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E8%80%85%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%BA%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%A7%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）罗伯特·欧文（Robert Owen）在19世纪初提出建立“新协和村”（New Har-mony）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E7%BD%97%E4%BC%AF%E7%89%B9%C2%B7%E6%AC%A7%E6%96%87%EF%BC%88Robert%20Owen%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A819%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E5%88%9D%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E2%80%9C%E6%96%B0%E5%8D%8F%E5%92%8C%E6%9D%91%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%88New%20Har-mony%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="他们的学说，把城市当作一个社会经济范畴，并为适应新的生活而变化。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%96%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%A6%E8%AF%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BD%93%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%8C%83%E7%95%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%BA%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%80%8C%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1898年英国人霍华德（Ebenezer Howard）提出“田园城市”理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1898%E5%B9%B4%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E9%9C%8D%E5%8D%8E%E5%BE%B7%EF%BC%88Ebenezer%20Howard%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E2%80%9C%E7%94%B0%E5%9B%AD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E2%80%9D%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在他的著作《明天——一条引向真正改革的和平道路》中提出“城市应与乡村结合”，他以一个“田园城市”的规划图解方案更具体地阐述其理论（图6-4）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%96%E7%9A%84%E8%91%97%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%8A%E6%98%8E%E5%A4%A9%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%A1%E5%BC%95%E5%90%91%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%AD%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%8E%E4%B9%A1%E6%9D%91%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%96%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E2%80%9C%E7%94%B0%E5%9B%AD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9B%BE%E8%A7%A3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%9B%B4%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E9%98%90%E8%BF%B0%E5%85%B6%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE6-4%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="规划人口3万人，占地400hm2。城市部分由一系列同心圆和6条放射线路组成，中心是占地20hm2的公园，沿公园可建公共建筑，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A33%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%A0%E5%9C%B0400hm2%E3%80%82%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%80%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E5%90%8C%E5%BF%83%E5%9C%86%E5%92%8C6%E6%9D%A1%E6%94%BE%E5%B0%84%E7%BA%BF%E8%B7%AF%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E6%98%AF%E5%8D%A0%E5%9C%B020hm2%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%BF%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E5%8F%AF%E5%BB%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="包括：市政厅、音乐厅、剧院、图书馆、医院等，它们的外面一圈是公园，公园外圈是商店，再外一圈是住宅，住宅外面是宽128m的林荫道，大道当中是学校、儿童游戏场及教堂，大道另一面又是一圈住宅。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%8E%85%E3%80%81%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E5%8E%85%E3%80%81%E5%89%A7%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E9%A6%86%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%88%E6%98%AF%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%88%E6%98%AF%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%96%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%88%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%A4%96%E9%9D%A2%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%BD128m%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%97%E8%8D%AB%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%93%E5%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E3%80%81%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%9C%BA%E5%8F%8A%E6%95%99%E5%A0%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%93%E5%8F%A6%E4%B8%80%E9%9D%A2%E5%8F%88%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%88%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市外围有2000hm2土地供农牧业生产。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%B4%E6%9C%892000hm2%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BE%9B%E5%86%9C%E7%89%A7%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="霍华德的理论把城市当作一个整体来研究，联系城乡关系，对人口密度、城市经济、城市绿化的重要性等问题提出了见解，对现代城市规划学科的建立起了重要作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9C%8D%E5%8D%8E%E5%BE%B7%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E6%8A%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BD%93%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%9D%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7%E7%AD%89%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%81%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E8%B5%B7%E4%BA%86%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="霍华德的这一理论受到了广泛重视，在英国也出现了两座以“田园城市”为名的建设实践，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9C%8D%E5%8D%8E%E5%BE%B7%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%80%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E5%8F%97%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%B9%BF%E6%B3%9B%E9%87%8D%E8%A7%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%9F%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%A4%E5%BA%A7%E4%BB%A5%E2%80%9C%E7%94%B0%E5%9B%AD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%BA%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="第一座是1903年伦敦东北的莱奇沃斯（Letchworth），" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E6%98%AF1903%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%A6%E6%95%A6%E4%B8%9C%E5%8C%97%E7%9A%84%E8%8E%B1%E5%A5%87%E6%B2%83%E6%96%AF%EF%BC%88Letchworth%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="第二座是1919年伦敦附近的韦林（Welwyn）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%BA%A7%E6%98%AF1919%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%A6%E6%95%A6%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%A6%E6%9E%97%EF%BC%88Welwyn%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.卫星城规划的理论与实践" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1898年霍华德（Ebenezer Howard）提出了“田园城市”理论，他的追随者雷蒙德·昂温（Raymond Unwin）进一步将其发展成为在大城市外围建立城镇，以疏散人口、控制大城市规模的理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1898%E5%B9%B4%E9%9C%8D%E5%8D%8E%E5%BE%B7%EF%BC%88Ebenezer%20Howard%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E7%94%B0%E5%9B%AD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E2%80%9D%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%96%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%BD%E9%9A%8F%E8%80%85%E9%9B%B7%E8%92%99%E5%BE%B7%C2%B7%E6%98%82%E6%B8%A9%EF%BC%88Raymond%20Unwin%EF%BC%89%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E5%B0%86%E5%85%B6%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%B4%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E3%80%81%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1915年，美国学者泰勒（Graham Romeyn Taylor）正式提出“卫星城”的概念，1918年他出版了《Satellite Cities:A Study of Industrial Suburbs》一书。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1915%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85%E6%B3%B0%E5%8B%92%EF%BC%88Graham%20Romeyn%20Taylor%EF%BC%89%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%EF%BC%8C1918%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%96%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8ASatellite%20Cities:A%20Study%20of%20Industrial%20Suburbs%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="同时期，美国规划师惠依顿也提出在大城市周围用绿地围起来，限制其发展，在绿地之外建设卫星城，设有工业企业并和大城市保持一定的联系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%88%E6%83%A0%E4%BE%9D%E9%A1%BF%E4%B9%9F%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E7%94%A8%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%B4%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%85%B6%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%BE%E6%9C%89%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%B9%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="卫星城的形成和发展经历了以下三个阶段：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%BB%8F%E5%8E%86%E4%BA%86%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="第一阶段卧城" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%8D%A7%E5%9F%8E%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="1912~1920年，巴黎制订了郊区的居住建设规划，意图在距巴黎16km的范围内建立28座居住城市；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1912~1920%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E5%88%B6%E8%AE%A2%E4%BA%86%E9%83%8A%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E6%84%8F%E5%9B%BE%E5%9C%A8%E8%B7%9D%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E16km%E7%9A%84%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E5%86%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B28%E5%BA%A7%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="这里没有生活服务设施，生产工作和文化生活的需求尚需去巴黎解决，一般称这种城镇为“卧城”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%92%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%B0%9A%E9%9C%80%E5%8E%BB%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E7%A7%B0%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%8D%A7%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="第二阶段半独立式卫星城" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E5%8D%8A%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%BC%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="1918年，芬兰建筑师伊利尔·沙里宁（Elie Saarinen）与荣格（Bertel Jung）为赫尔辛基新区明克尼米-哈格（Munkkiniemi-Haaga，制订了一个17万人口的规划方案，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1918%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E8%8A%AC%E5%85%B0%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%8A%E5%88%A9%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E6%B2%99%E9%87%8C%E5%AE%81%EF%BC%88Elie%20Saarinen%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%8E%E8%8D%A3%E6%A0%BC%EF%BC%88Bertel%20Jung%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%BA%E8%B5%AB%E5%B0%94%E8%BE%9B%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%8C%BA%E6%98%8E%E5%85%8B%E5%B0%BC%E7%B1%B3-%E5%93%88%E6%A0%BC%EF%BC%88Munkkiniemi-Haaga%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%B6%E8%AE%A2%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA17%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="因该方案远远超出了当时的财政经济和政治处理能力，故其中只有一小部分得以实施。该规划方案体现了沙里宁提出的“有机疏散”理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%A0%E8%AF%A5%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E8%BF%9C%E8%BF%9C%E8%B6%85%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%BD%93%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A2%E6%94%BF%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%92%8C%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%85%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%B0%8F%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%BE%97%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%E8%AF%A5%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%B2%99%E9%87%8C%E5%AE%81%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3%E2%80%9D%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="这类卫星城不同于“卧城”，除了居住建筑外，还设有一定数量的工厂及服务设施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E7%B1%BB%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8E%E2%80%9C%E5%8D%A7%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E8%AE%BE%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E5%8E%82%E5%8F%8A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="第三阶段独立式卫星城" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%BC%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="（1）20世纪40年代" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%8920%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA40%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1946年（英）斯蒂夫尼奇（Stevenage），它开辟了完整步行街的先例。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1946%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E8%8B%B1%EF%BC%89%E6%96%AF%E8%92%82%E5%A4%AB%E5%B0%BC%E5%A5%87%EF%BC%88Stevenage%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E5%BC%80%E8%BE%9F%E4%BA%86%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E8%A1%97%E7%9A%84%E5%85%88%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1947年（英）哈洛（Harlow），由《市镇设计》的作者吉伯德（F.Gibberd）规划，在哈洛新城中，佩里（C.Perry）有关“邻里单位”的理论得以实现；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1947%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E8%8B%B1%EF%BC%89%E5%93%88%E6%B4%9B%EF%BC%88Harlow%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E3%80%8A%E5%B8%82%E9%95%87%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E5%90%89%E4%BC%AF%E5%BE%B7%EF%BC%88F.Gibberd%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%93%88%E6%B4%9B%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%A9%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%88C.Perry%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E2%80%9C%E9%82%BB%E9%87%8C%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E5%BE%97%E4%BB%A5%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1947.年（英）考文垂（Coventry），考文垂的步行街以开敞的楼梯及连廊连接二层商场，并分隔成院落。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1947.%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E8%8B%B1%EF%BC%89%E8%80%83%E6%96%87%E5%9E%82%EF%BC%88Coventry%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%83%E6%96%87%E5%9E%82%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E8%A1%97%E4%BB%A5%E5%BC%80%E6%95%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF%E5%8F%8A%E8%BF%9E%E5%BB%8A%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E4%BA%8C%E5%B1%82%E5%95%86%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94%E6%88%90%E9%99%A2%E8%90%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="其中，哈洛是英国第一代卫星城的代表。同一时期，还有法国的勒阿弗尔（Le Havre）；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%93%88%E6%B4%9B%E6%98%AF%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%82%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%8B%92%E9%98%BF%E5%BC%97%E5%B0%94%EF%BC%88Le%20Havre%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="该城由佩雷（Auguste Perret）规划设计，受法国建筑师加尼埃（Tony Garnier）“工业城市”的影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AF%A5%E5%9F%8E%E7%94%B1%E4%BD%A9%E9%9B%B7%EF%BC%88Auguste%20Perret%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%97%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%8A%A0%E5%B0%BC%E5%9F%83%EF%BC%88Tony%20Garnier%EF%BC%89%E2%80%9C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="（2）20世纪50年代" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%8920%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA50%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1950年（瑞典）魏林比（Vallinby），它是斯德哥尔摩的六个卫星城镇之一，距母城16公里。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1950%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E7%91%9E%E5%85%B8%EF%BC%89%E9%AD%8F%E6%9E%97%E6%AF%94%EF%BC%88Vallinby%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E6%98%AF%E6%96%AF%E5%BE%B7%E5%93%A5%E5%B0%94%E6%91%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%AA%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%B7%9D%E6%AF%8D%E5%9F%8E16%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="与这个时期的其他卫星城不同，它对母城有较大的依赖性，是半独立式的卫星城。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%8D%E5%9F%8E%E6%9C%89%E8%BE%83%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%8D%8A%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="1956年（英）坎伯诺尔德（Cumbernauld），是位于英国北部苏格兰格拉斯哥附近的一座新城，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1956%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E8%8B%B1%EF%BC%89%E5%9D%8E%E4%BC%AF%E8%AF%BA%E5%B0%94%E5%BE%B7%EF%BC%88Cumbernauld%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%8C%97%E9%83%A8%E8%8B%8F%E6%A0%BC%E5%85%B0%E6%A0%BC%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E5%93%A5%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="坎伯诺尔德是英国第二代卫星城的代表，其住宅建筑群环绕布置在市中心周边，与市中心保持尽可能短的距离。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9D%8E%E4%BC%AF%E8%AF%BA%E5%B0%94%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%AF%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%A3%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BE%A4%E7%8E%AF%E7%BB%95%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%9C%A8%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%91%A8%E8%BE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E5%B0%BD%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E7%9F%AD%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="（3）20世纪60年代" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%8920%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA60%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1965年（法）塞尔吉-蓬图瓦兹（Cergy-Pontoise），同一时期在巴黎外围一共建了5座新城，现塞尔吉与蓬图瓦兹已经合并为一座城市。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1965%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%89%E5%A1%9E%E5%B0%94%E5%90%89-%E8%93%AC%E5%9B%BE%E7%93%A6%E5%85%B9%EF%BC%88Cergy-Pontoise%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%E5%9C%A8%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%B4%E4%B8%80%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%865%E5%BA%A7%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%B0%E5%A1%9E%E5%B0%94%E5%90%89%E4%B8%8E%E8%93%AC%E5%9B%BE%E7%93%A6%E5%85%B9%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E5%90%88%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1967年（英）米尔顿-凯恩斯（Milton-Keynes），位于英格兰中部，为英国的经济重镇，还是英国新城镇建设的成功典范；米尔顿-凯恩斯是英国第三代卫星城的代表。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1967%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%88%E8%8B%B1%EF%BC%89%E7%B1%B3%E5%B0%94%E9%A1%BF-%E5%87%AF%E6%81%A9%E6%96%AF%EF%BC%88Milton-Keynes%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E8%8B%B1%E6%A0%BC%E5%85%B0%E4%B8%AD%E9%83%A8%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E9%87%8D%E9%95%87%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E5%85%B8%E8%8C%83%EF%BC%9B%E7%B1%B3%E5%B0%94%E9%A1%BF-%E5%87%AF%E6%81%A9%E6%96%AF%E6%98%AF%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E4%BB%A3%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="现阶段的卫星城，为多中心敞开式城市结构，用高速交通线把卫星城和主城联系起来，主城的功能扩散到卫星城中去。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%B0%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E6%95%9E%E5%BC%80%E5%BC%8F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%BA%BF%E6%8A%8A%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%BB%E5%9F%8E%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E5%9F%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%89%A9%E6%95%A3%E5%88%B0%E5%8D%AB%E6%98%9F%E5%9F%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="为了控制大城市人口过分膨胀，疏散大城市的部分工业和人口，同时也是为了抵消大城市对周围地区人口的吸引力。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%BF%87%E5%88%86%E8%86%A8%E8%83%80%EF%BC%8C%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%8A%B5%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AF%B9%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="3.《雅典宪章》与《马丘比丘宪章》" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E3%80%8A%E9%9B%85%E5%85%B8%E5%AE%AA%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%8E%E3%80%8A%E9%A9%AC%E4%B8%98%E6%AF%94%E4%B8%98%E5%AE%AA%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1922年勒·柯布西耶写了《明日的城市》一书，提出了巴黎改造方案。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1922%E5%B9%B4%E5%8B%92%C2%B7%E6%9F%AF%E5%B8%83%E8%A5%BF%E8%80%B6%E5%86%99%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8A%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%A6%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="主张减少市中心的建筑密度、增加人口密度。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E5%BC%A0%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="建筑向高层发展，增加道路宽度及两旁的空地、绿地，大胆改变大城市的传统形式的结构布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%90%91%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%A4%E6%97%81%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%83%86%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="1933年国际现代建筑协会（CIAM）在雅典开会，制定了《城市规划大纲》，后称为《雅典宪章》。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1933%E5%B9%B4%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8D%8F%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%88CIAM%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%85%E5%85%B8%E5%BC%80%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%A4%A7%E7%BA%B2%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%8A%E9%9B%85%E5%85%B8%E5%AE%AA%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="大纲首先提出城市要与其周围影响地区作为一个整体来研究，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A7%E7%BA%B2%E9%A6%96%E5%85%88%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%B6%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%9D%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="城市规划的目的是解决居住、工作、游憩与交通四大活动功能的正常运行）城市规划的核心是解决好城市功能分区。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%81%E6%B8%B8%E6%86%A9%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%98%AF%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%A5%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="1978年12月，一批著名的建筑师、规划师在秘鲁的利马集会，对《雅典宪章》的实践做了评价，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1978%E5%B9%B412%E6%9C%88%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%89%B9%E8%91%97%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%88%E5%9C%A8%E7%A7%98%E9%B2%81%E7%9A%84%E5%88%A9%E9%A9%AC%E9%9B%86%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E3%80%8A%E9%9B%85%E5%85%B8%E5%AE%AA%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%86%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="认为《雅典宪章》的某些原则是正确的，但认为城市规划追求功能分区的办法，忽略了城市中人与人之间多方面的联系而应创造一个综合的、多功能的生活环境。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%8A%E9%9B%85%E5%85%B8%E5%AE%AA%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%9F%90%E4%BA%9B%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5%E4%BA%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E8%80%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E3%80%81%E5%A4%9A%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="同时提出，私人车辆要服从公共运输系统的发展，要注意在发展交通与能源“危机”之间取得平衡，提出了生活环境与自然环境的和谐问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E8%BD%A6%E8%BE%86%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%B8%8E%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E2%80%9C%E5%8D%B1%E6%9C%BA%E2%80%9D%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="会后发表了《马丘比丘宪章》，其中还提出了生活环境与自然环境的和谐问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BC%9A%E5%90%8E%E5%8F%91%E8%A1%A8%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8A%E9%A9%AC%E4%B8%98%E6%AF%94%E4%B8%98%E5%AE%AA%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E8%BF%98%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="4.邻里单位与小区规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E9%82%BB%E9%87%8C%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E4%B8%8E%E5%B0%8F%E5%8C%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="20世纪30年代在美欧相继提出“邻里单位”的居住区规划理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA30%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%B8%E7%BB%A7%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E2%80%9C%E9%82%BB%E9%87%8C%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="“邻里单位”是组成居住区的基本单元，其中设置小学使幼儿上学不穿越马路，并以此控制与计算人口和用地规模，后来考虑了设置日常生活需要的公共设施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E9%82%BB%E9%87%8C%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E2%80%9D%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A6%E4%BD%BF%E5%B9%BC%E5%84%BF%E4%B8%8A%E5%AD%A6%E4%B8%8D%E7%A9%BF%E8%B6%8A%E9%A9%AC%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%A4%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%8E%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%92%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8E%E6%9D%A5%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E4%BA%86%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="第二次世界大战后，欧洲发展为“小区规划”理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%B0%8F%E5%8C%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E2%80%9D%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="一般按交通干道划分小区成为居住区构成的基本单元，把居住建筑、公共建筑、绿地等进行综合安排，一般的生活服务可在小区内解决。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%8C%89%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%93%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E5%B0%8F%E5%8C%BA%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%8A%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8F%AF%E5%9C%A8%E5%B0%8F%E5%8C%BA%E5%86%85%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="5.有机疏散理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5.%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="为解决城市膨胀而产生的“城市病”，伊利尔·沙里宁在1943年发表的《城市一它的发展、衰败与未来》一书中完善了有机疏散理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%86%A8%E8%83%80%E8%80%8C%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%97%85%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%8A%E5%88%A9%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E6%B2%99%E9%87%8C%E5%AE%81%E5%9C%A81943%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%91%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%81%E8%A1%B0%E8%B4%A5%E4%B8%8E%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B9%A6%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%E4%BA%86%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="他从生物有机体的细胞成长现象中受到启示，认为把扩大的城市范围划分为不同的集中点所使用的区域，这种区域内又可分为不同活动所需要的地段。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%96%E4%BB%8E%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E6%88%90%E9%95%BF%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%97%E5%88%B0%E5%90%AF%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A4%E4%B8%BA%E6%8A%8A%E6%89%A9%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%82%B9%E6%89%80%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%86%85%E5%8F%88%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E6%89%80%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="他是把无秩序的集中变为有秩序的分散，把密集地区分为一个个的集镇或地区，彼此之间用绿化带分隔，以便城市居民接近大自然。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%96%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%8A%E6%97%A0%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%BA%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%EF%BC%8C%E6%8A%8A%E5%AF%86%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%AA%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%86%E9%95%87%E6%88%96%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%BC%E6%AD%A4%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%94%A8%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E5%B8%A6%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%BF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="6.区域规划和国土规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E6.%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="城市的日益发展和城市问题的复杂化，使人们认识到不能就城市论城市，必须从区域、国土的范围来研究有关社会、经济、资源、交通等各方面问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E7%9B%8A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%B0%B1%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%BB%8E%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E6%9D%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%AD%89%E5%90%84%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="从地区着眼，对社会、经济的发展和生产力分布进行整体思考和规划调节。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%8E%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9D%80%E7%9C%BC%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%92%8C%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%8A%9B%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="西方区域规划理论从20世纪后期发展起来，英国格迪斯提出了集合城市（组团城市）和区域规划概念。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%BB%8E20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E5%90%8E%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E6%A0%BC%E8%BF%AA%E6%96%AF%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%88%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%A2%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="欧美一些国家实行了经济区规划，大城市也把区域作为一个经济单位、社会单位和城市体系来研究，并进行了大城市地区的规划。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AC%A7%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%86%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8C%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B9%9F%E6%8A%8A%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E6%9D%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="（三）城市规划学科的新发展" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="通过深入的科学研究，科学地预测未来，不断地及时地调节和完善城市规划。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%9C%B0%E9%A2%84%E6%B5%8B%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%AD%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E6%97%B6%E5%9C%B0%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="规划学科的发展主要表现在如下方面：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="1.宏观研究的扩展与微观研究的深入" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%82%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E4%B8%8E%E5%BE%AE%E8%A7%82%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="城市规划，在宏观上从形体扩展到社会、经济及城市之间、城乡之间与城市体系的宏观问题；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%8A%E4%BB%8E%E5%BD%A2%E4%BD%93%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E5%88%B0%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8F%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%82%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="在微观上深入研究住房、就业、交通、社会服务等问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%BE%AE%E8%A7%82%E4%B8%8A%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%BF%E3%80%81%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%AD%89%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="2.交叉科学研究城市问题" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="各种学科的交叉，丰富更新本学科的理论与实践、更广泛地应用新的科学技术手段。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%9C%AC%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E3%80%81%E6%9B%B4%E5%B9%BF%E6%B3%9B%E5%9C%B0%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="如系统论、控制论、信息论及计算机、数理分析、遥感遥测等新观念、新技术在城市规划中应用等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%81%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%81%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E8%AE%BA%E5%8F%8A%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E3%80%81%E6%95%B0%E7%90%86%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%81%E9%81%A5%E6%84%9F%E9%81%A5%E6%B5%8B%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B0%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%81%E6%96%B0%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="3.重视城市规划的时间要素" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E9%87%8D%E8%A7%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="通过城市的产生、发展、兴衰的变化规律，研究历史与现状。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%81%E5%85%B4%E8%A1%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E8%A7%84%E5%BE%8B%EF%BC%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="20世纪60年代以来，世界范围内社会、经济的战略思想转变和更新，对城市规划的理论和实践提出了新的要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA60%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E4%BB%A5%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E5%86%85%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%98%E5%92%8C%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="4.可持续发展的概念" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="1978年联合国世界环境与发展大会第一次在在国际社会正式提出“可持续发展”的观念。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1978%E5%B9%B4%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%A4%A7%E4%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E2%80%9C%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E2%80%9D%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="1987年联合国世界环境与发展委员会发表了《我们共同的未来》，全面阐述了可持续发展的理念，核心是实现经济、社会和环境之间的协调发展，它的影响已成为全球共识和指导各国社会经济发展的总原则。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1987%E5%B9%B4%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%A7%94%E5%91%98%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E8%A1%A8%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8A%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E9%98%90%E8%BF%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%98%AF%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%85%B1%E8%AF%86%E5%92%8C%E6%8C%87%E5%AF%BC%E5%90%84%E5%9B%BD%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="它具有现代意义的发展观，它所追求的是社会、经济和环境目标的协调统一，给后人的生存与发展留有余地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%83%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E6%89%80%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%99%E5%90%8E%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%95%99%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%99%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市化的快速发展带来了巨大的社会效益和经济效益，但也造成广泛的“城市病”，面对错综复杂的城市问题，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E4%BA%86%E5%B7%A8%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E4%B9%9F%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%B9%BF%E6%B3%9B%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%97%85%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%AF%B9%E9%94%99%E7%BB%BC%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="可持续发展的战略思想要求转变建筑与城市规划的狭义认识和传统理念，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%98%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E7%8B%AD%E4%B9%89%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86%E5%92%8C%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="适应时代发展的需要，要研究社会、经济、环境、资源、文化等方面的综合发展目标，纳入到统一的城乡发展规划中来，落实到物质环境的建设上，从而促进城市可持续发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%B3%E5%85%A5%E5%88%B0%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E8%90%BD%E5%AE%9E%E5%88%B0%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E8%80%8C%E4%BF%83%E8%BF%9B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="例如环境保护是城市发展的组成部分，环境质量是发展水平和发展质量的根本标志，环境权利和环境义务是一致的、统一的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%9D%83%E5%88%A9%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B9%89%E5%8A%A1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E7%9A%84%E3%80%81%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="5.人居环境科学" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5.%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%85%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="人居环境科学是为建筑更符合人类理想的聚居环境，在20世纪下半叶国际上逐渐发展起来的一门综合性学科。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%85%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%9B%B4%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3%E7%9A%84%E8%81%9A%E5%B1%85%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A820%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8A%E5%8F%B6%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E4%B8%8A%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E9%97%A8%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%80%A7%E5%AD%A6%E7%A7%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="它以包括乡村、集镇、城市等在内的所有人类聚居环境为研究对象，着重研究人与环境之间的相互关系，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%83%E4%BB%A5%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B9%A1%E6%9D%91%E3%80%81%E9%9B%86%E9%95%87%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%A8%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E8%81%9A%E5%B1%85%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%BA%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E7%9D%80%E9%87%8D%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="强调把人类聚居作为一个整体，从政治、社会、文化、技术等方面，全面地、系统地、综合地加以研究，促使人居环境的可持续发展，使人类生存环境越来越美好。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E6%8A%8A%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E8%81%9A%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%83%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%85%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%B6%8A%E6%9D%A5%E8%B6%8A%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="6.建设生态城市" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E6.%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="为了摆脱城市负面困扰，使人们充分享受城市的优越条件，20世纪下半叶出现生态城市概念。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%91%86%E8%84%B1%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%B4%9F%E9%9D%A2%E5%9B%B0%E6%89%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E5%8F%97%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%98%E8%B6%8A%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C20%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8A%E5%8F%B6%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="根据生态学理论，人们认识到自然环境是一个庞大、复杂的生态系统，人类本身是其中一个组成部分，只有保持系统各部分的平衡，人类生存的载体及其本身才能持续发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%AD%A6%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86%E5%88%B0%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%BA%9E%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%81%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E6%9C%AC%E8%BA%AB%E6%98%AF%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%90%84%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E7%9A%84%E8%BD%BD%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E6%9C%AC%E8%BA%AB%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%8C%81%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="节能减排、防控大气升温、保护地球、保护物种，已成为全人类的共同任务；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%8A%82%E8%83%BD%E5%87%8F%E6%8E%92%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%8E%A7%E5%A4%A7%E6%B0%94%E5%8D%87%E6%B8%A9%E3%80%81%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E3%80%81%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%89%A9%E7%A7%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%85%A8%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="因此，城市发展有利于环境生态，与自然环境和谐发展，才是正确的最高标准。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="建设生态城市，按照生态学的规律来规划城市、建设城市和改造城市。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%BE%8B%E6%9D%A5%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%92%8C%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="7.“全球城”理论" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E7.%E2%80%9C%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%9D%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="发达国家在20世纪70年代完成了城市化进程（城市化水平≥70%），步入后城市化阶段。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%91%E8%BE%BE%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%9C%A820%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA70%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%96%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%88%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%96%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E2%89%A570%25%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A5%E5%85%A5%E5%90%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%96%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="80年代的世界经济的发展，90年代信息技术的革命，相继出现了“全球城”和全球化理论。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E80%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%EF%BC%8C%E7%9B%B8%E7%BB%A7%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9C%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%9D%E5%92%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%8C%96%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="世界经济结构变化，资本、劳动力、产业及经济中心全球性的流动、迁移、集聚促使全球城市体系的多极化。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E8%B5%84%E6%9C%AC%E3%80%81%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E5%8F%8A%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%81%E5%8A%A8%E3%80%81%E8%BF%81%E7%A7%BB%E3%80%81%E9%9B%86%E8%81%9A%E4%BF%83%E4%BD%BF%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E6%9E%81%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="建筑综合体实现更高效率，以跨国集团总部为标志的“全球城”开始出现。在世界各地具有国际性质的大城市，纷纷建起了具有国际意义的中央商务区，即“CBD”。地方建筑传统受到挑战。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E4%BD%93%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%9B%B4%E9%AB%98%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E8%B7%A8%E5%9B%BD%E9%9B%86%E5%9B%A2%E6%80%BB%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%BA%E6%A0%87%E5%BF%97%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%9F%8E%E2%80%9D%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%82%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%B7%E7%BA%B7%E5%BB%BA%E8%B5%B7%E4%BA%86%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A1%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E2%80%9CCBD%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E5%8F%97%E5%88%B0%E6%8C%91%E6%88%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="8.北京宪章" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E8.%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%AA%E7%AB%A0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="1999年6月，国际建筑师协会（UIA）第20届世界建筑师大会在北京召开，大会一致通过了吴良铺院士起草的《北京宪章》，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1999%E5%B9%B46%E6%9C%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%8D%8F%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%88UIA%EF%BC%89%E7%AC%AC20%E5%B1%8A%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%88%E5%A4%A7%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%8F%AC%E5%BC%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%A7%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E4%BA%86%E5%90%B4%E8%89%AF%E9%93%BA%E9%99%A2%E5%A3%AB%E8%B5%B7%E8%8D%89%E7%9A%84%E3%80%8A%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%AA%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="《北京宪章》总结了百年来建筑发展的历程，并在剖析和整合20世纪的历史与现实、理论与实践、成就与问题及各种新思路和新观点的基础上，展望了21世纪建筑学的前进方向。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%AA%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%8B%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93%E4%BA%86%E7%99%BE%E5%B9%B4%E6%9D%A5%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%86%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%9C%A8%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B4%E5%90%8820%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E3%80%81%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E3%80%81%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%8E%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%8F%8A%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B0%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF%E5%92%8C%E6%96%B0%E8%A7%82%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B%E4%BA%8621%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8D%E8%BF%9B%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="（四）当代城市规划思想方法的变革" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%93%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%98%E9%9D%A9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="社会、经济、文化的发展变化是思想方法变革的基础。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E6%98%AF%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%98%E9%9D%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="（1）由单向的封闭思想方法，转向复合发散型的思想方法。包括系统内外的多条思维和反馈。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E7%94%B1%E5%8D%95%E5%90%91%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%81%E9%97%AD%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E8%BD%AC%E5%90%91%E5%A4%8D%E5%90%88%E5%8F%91%E6%95%A3%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%86%85%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E6%9D%A1%E6%80%9D%E7%BB%B4%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%8D%E9%A6%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="（2）由静态最终理想状态的思想方法转向动态过程的思想方法。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E7%94%B1%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E6%9C%80%E7%BB%88%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%BD%AC%E5%90%91%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="（3）由刚性规划的思想方法转向弹性规划的思想方法。刚性思想缺乏多种选择性，弹性规划表现在规模、时效期和用地形态上的必要弹性等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E7%94%B1%E5%88%9A%E6%80%A7%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%BD%AC%E5%90%91%E5%BC%B9%E6%80%A7%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%E5%88%9A%E6%80%A7%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E7%BC%BA%E4%B9%8F%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%B9%E6%80%A7%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E6%97%B6%E6%95%88%E6%9C%9F%E5%92%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%B9%E6%80%A7%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="（4）由指令性的思想方法，转向引导性的思想方法。指令思想是把城市规划看作控制发展的枢纽；引导性是强调规划在城市发展过程的引导作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E7%94%B1%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E8%BD%AC%E5%90%91%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9C%8B%E4%BD%9C%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%A2%E7%BA%BD%EF%BC%9B%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC%E6%80%A7%E6%98%AF%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="第二节   城乡规划的工作内容" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="城市总体规划、控制性详细规划、修建性详细规划的基础资料收集内容及要求详见《城市规划基础资料搜集规范》GB/T50831-2012。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8F%8A%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%81%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E6%90%9C%E9%9B%86%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E3%80%8BGB/T50831-2012%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）城市规划的调查研究与基础资料" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="调研是城市规划的基础。通过调研，弄清城市发展的历史、地理、自然、文化的背景及社会经济发展的状况和条件，找出决定城市建设发展的主要矛盾。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%B0%83%E7%A0%94%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E3%80%82%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E8%B0%83%E7%A0%94%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%84%E6%B8%85%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E7%8A%B6%E5%86%B5%E5%92%8C%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%BE%E5%87%BA%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）城乡规划的层面" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%82%E9%9D%A2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="根据我国《城乡规划法》，城乡规划包括城镇体系规划、城市规划、镇规划、乡规划和村庄规划。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E6%9D%91%E5%BA%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市规划、镇规划分为总体规划和详细规划。详细规划分为控制性详细规划和修建性详细规划。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="规划区是指城市、镇和村庄的建成区以及因城乡建设和发展需要，必须实行规划控制的区域。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8C%BA%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E5%92%8C%E6%9D%91%E5%BA%84%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%90%E5%8C%BA%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%9B%A0%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E5%AE%9E%E8%A1%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="根据规划工作的实际需要，在正式编制城乡规划前，应由城市人民政府组织制定城乡规划纲要。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%89%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E7%94%B1%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%BA%B2%E8%A6%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="对城乡发展需要确定的主要目标、方向和内容提出原则性意见，作为规划编制的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E3%80%81%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E5%92%8C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E6%80%A7%E6%84%8F%E8%A7%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（三）城乡规划各阶段的工作内容" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%90%84%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.城乡规划纲要" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%BA%B2%E8%A6%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="主要内容包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）市域城镇体系规划纲要。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%9F%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%BA%B2%E8%A6%81%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="内容包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="提出市域城乡统筹发展战略；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%9F%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%BB%9F%E7%AD%B9%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="确定生态环境、土地和水资源、能源、自然和历史文化遗产保护等方面的综合目标和保护要求，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%B4%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%92%8C%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="提出空间管制原则；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B6%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="预测市域总人口及城镇化水平，确定各城镇人口规模、职能分工、空间布局方案和建设标准；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%A2%84%E6%B5%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%9F%E6%80%BB%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%8A%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E5%8C%96%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%84%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E8%81%8C%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="原则确定市域交通发展策略。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%9F%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）提出城市规划区范围。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8C%BA%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）分析城市职能，提出城市性质和发展目标。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%81%8C%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）提出禁区建、限建区、适建区范围。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%A6%81%E5%8C%BA%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%81%E9%99%90%E5%BB%BA%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E9%80%82%E5%BB%BA%E5%8C%BA%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）预测城市人口规模。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E9%A2%84%E6%B5%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（6）研究中心城区空间增长边界，提出建设用地规模和建设用地范围。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%9F%8E%E5%8C%BA%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E8%BE%B9%E7%95%8C%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（7）提出交通发展战略及主要对外交通设施布局原则。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（8）提出重大基础设施和公共服务设施的发展目标乳" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E4%B9%B3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（9）提出建立综合防灾体系的原则和建设方针。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%889%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E9%98%B2%E7%81%BE%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%B9%E9%92%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="纲要成果以文字为主，辅以示意性图纸。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BA%B2%E8%A6%81%E6%88%90%E6%9E%9C%E4%BB%A5%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%EF%BC%8C%E8%BE%85%E4%BB%A5%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F%E6%80%A7%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="图纸比例为1/10万~1/2.5万。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA1/10%E4%B8%87~1/2.5%E4%B8%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.城镇体系规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城镇体系规划的内容包括：城镇空间布局和规模控制，重大基础设施的布局，为保护生态环境、资源等需要严格控制的区域。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%AD%89%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%A5%E6%A0%BC%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="具体规划工作内容是：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）摸清市、镇域的基本情况，分析发展条件、优势和制约因素，提出发展战略及目标。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%91%B8%E6%B8%85%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%81%E4%BC%98%E5%8A%BF%E5%92%8C%E5%88%B6%E7%BA%A6%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%88%98%E7%95%A5%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）市、镇域城镇化水平和途径的预测；提出城镇体系的规模结构、职能分工和空间布局；提出近期发展的重点和生产力布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E5%9F%9F%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E5%8C%96%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%92%8C%E9%80%94%E5%BE%84%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%84%E6%B5%8B%EF%BC%9B%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E3%80%81%E8%81%8C%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%92%8C%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%9B%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E5%92%8C%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%8A%9B%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）确定区域基础设施的发展目标及布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E5%8F%8A%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）提出实施规划的技术、经济政策和措施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="市域城镇体系规划图的图纸比例为1/5万~1/10万。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%9F%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9B%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA1/5%E4%B8%87~1/10%E4%B8%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.城市总体规划、镇总体规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市总体规划、镇总体规划的内容应当包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="城市、镇的发展布局，功能分区，用地布局、综合交通体系，禁止、限制和适宜建设和地域范围，各类专项规划等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E3%80%81%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E9%80%82%E5%AE%9C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%9F%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%93%E9%A1%B9%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="应当作为城市总体规划、镇总体规划的强制性内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="规划区范围、规划区内建设用地规模、基础设施和公共服务设施用地、水源地和水系、基本农田和绿化用地、环境保护、自然与历史文化遗产保护以及防灾减灾等内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8C%BA%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8C%BA%E5%86%85%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%B4%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%86%9C%E7%94%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E3%80%81%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E9%98%B2%E7%81%BE%E5%87%8F%E7%81%BE%E7%AD%89%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="城市总体规划、镇总体规划的规划期限一般为20年。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%B8%BA20%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市总体规划还应当对城市更长远的发展作出预测性安排。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%BF%98%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9B%B4%E9%95%BF%E8%BF%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%BD%9C%E5%87%BA%E9%A2%84%E6%B5%8B%E6%80%A7%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2005年12月31日建设部发布了《城市规划编制办法》（以下简称《编制办法》）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2005%E5%B9%B412%E6%9C%8831%E6%97%A5%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%83%A8%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%AE%80%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%8A%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="《编制办法》提出的城市总体规划的强制性内容主要包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）城市规划区范围。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8C%BA%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）市域内应当控制开发的地域。包括：基本农田保护区，风景名胜区，湿地、水源保护区等生态敏感区，地下矿产资源分布地区。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%9F%E5%86%85%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%9F%E3%80%82%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%86%9C%E7%94%B0%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%90%8D%E8%83%9C%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%B9%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%8C%BA%E7%AD%89%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E7%9F%BF%E4%BA%A7%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）城市建设用地。包括：规划期限内城市建设用地的发展规模，土地使用强度管制区划和相应的控制指标（建设用地面积、容积率、人口容量等），城市各类绿地的具体布局，城市地下空间开发布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90%E5%86%85%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%BA%E5%BA%A6%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B6%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%88%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E3%80%81%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%AF%E7%8E%87%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）城市基础设施和公共服务设施。包括：城市干道系统网络、城市轨道交通网络、交通枢纽布局，城市水源地及其保护区范围和其他重大市政基础设施，文化、教育、卫生、体育等方面主要公共服务设施的布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%BD%A8%E9%81%93%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%9E%A2%E7%BA%BD%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%8C%BA%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E3%80%81%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E7%AD%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）城市历史文化遗产保护。包括：历史文化保护的具体控制指标和规定，历史文化街区、历史建筑、重要地下文物埋藏区的具体位置和界线。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E3%80%82%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E8%A1%97%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%9F%8B%E8%97%8F%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%92%8C%E7%95%8C%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（6）生态环境保护与建设目标，污染控制与治理措施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%8E%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（7）城市防灾工程。包括：城市防洪标准、防洪堤走向，城市抗震与消防疏散通道，城市人防设施布局，地质灾害防护规定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%98%B2%E7%81%BE%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E3%80%82%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E5%A0%A4%E8%B5%B0%E5%90%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%8A%97%E9%9C%87%E4%B8%8E%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3%E9%80%9A%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E9%98%B2%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E7%81%BE%E5%AE%B3%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="以上内容是编制城市总体规划必须涉及的内容，而且不能有缺项，尤其是后两项内容极为重要，对于建设宜居城市、安全城市必不可少。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%AF%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E7%BC%BA%E9%A1%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%A4%E5%85%B6%E6%98%AF%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%A4%E9%A1%B9%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%9E%81%E4%B8%BA%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%AE%9C%E5%B1%85%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BF%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="总体规划文件包括规划文本及附件，规划说明及基础资料收入附件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%8A%E9%99%84%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%8A%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E9%99%84%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="图纸包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="城市现状图、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="市域城镇体系规划图、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%9F%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="城市总体规划图、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="道路交通规划图、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="各项专业规划图及" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9B%BE%E5%8F%8A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="近期建设规划图。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="图纸比例大中城市为1/25000~1/10000，小城镇1/10000~1/5000。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%BA1/25000~1/10000%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%8F%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%871/10000~1/5000%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="4.乡规划、村庄规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E6%9D%91%E5%BA%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="乡规划、村庄规划应当从农村实际出发，尊重村民意愿，体现地方和农村特色。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E6%9D%91%E5%BA%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E4%BB%8E%E5%86%9C%E6%9D%91%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E6%9D%91%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E6%84%BF%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E5%92%8C%E5%86%9C%E6%9D%91%E7%89%B9%E8%89%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="乡规划、村庄规划的内容应当包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E6%9D%91%E5%BA%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="规划区范围，住宅、道路、供水、排水、供电、垃圾收集、畜禽养殖场所等农村生产、生活服务设施、公益事业等各项建设用地布局、建设要求，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8C%BA%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E3%80%81%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E4%BE%9B%E7%94%B5%E3%80%81%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E3%80%81%E7%95%9C%E7%A6%BD%E5%85%BB%E6%AE%96%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E7%AD%89%E5%86%9C%E6%9D%91%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E7%9B%8A%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%9A%E7%AD%89%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="以及对耕地等自然资源和历史文化遗产保护、防灾减灾等的具体安排。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%AF%B9%E8%80%95%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E5%92%8C%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E7%81%BE%E5%87%8F%E7%81%BE%E7%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="乡规划还应当包括本行政区域内的村庄发展布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%BF%98%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%9C%AC%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%91%E5%BA%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="5.详细规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5.%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）控制性详细规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="《编制办法》对控制性详细规划的内容提出以下明确要求：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%E5%AF%B9%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）确定规划范围内不同性质用地的界线，确定各类用地内适建、不适建或者有条件地允许建设的建筑类型。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E5%86%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%95%8C%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%86%85%E9%80%82%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%E5%BB%BA%E6%88%96%E8%80%85%E6%9C%89%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）确定各地块建筑高度、建筑密度、容积率、绿地率等控制指标；确定公共设施配套要求、交通出入口方位、停车泊位、建筑后退红线距离等要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%97%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%AF%E7%8E%87%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%8E%87%E7%AD%89%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%9B%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E9%85%8D%E5%A5%97%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3%E6%96%B9%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E6%B3%8A%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%90%8E%E9%80%80%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E7%AD%89%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3）提出各地块的建筑体量、体形、色彩等城市设计指导原则。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%97%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8F%E3%80%81%E4%BD%93%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%81%E8%89%B2%E5%BD%A9%E7%AD%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%8C%87%E5%AF%BC%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4）根据交通需求分析，确定地块出入口位置、停车泊位、公共交通场站用地范围和站点位置、步行交通以及其他交通设施。规定各级道路的红线、断面、交叉口形式及渠化措施、控制点坐标和标高。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%97%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E6%B3%8A%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%9C%BA%E7%AB%99%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E5%92%8C%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%81%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%84%E7%BA%A7%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%81%E6%96%AD%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E5%8F%A3%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%8A%E6%B8%A0%E5%8C%96%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%82%B9%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%87%E9%AB%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="5）根据规划建设容量，确定市政工程管线位置、管径和工程设施的用地界线，进行管线综合；确定地下空间开发利用的具体要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5%EF%BC%89%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E7%AE%A1%E7%BA%BF%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E5%BE%84%E5%92%8C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%95%8C%E7%BA%BF%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%AE%A1%E7%BA%BF%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%EF%BC%9B%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="6）制定相应的土地使用与建筑管理规定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E6%EF%BC%89%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="另外，控制性详细规划确定的各地块的主要用途、建筑密度、建筑高度、容积率、绿地率、基础设施和公共服务设施配套规定应当作为强制性内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%97%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E5%AE%B9%E7%A7%AF%E7%8E%87%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%8E%87%E3%80%81%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E9%85%8D%E5%A5%97%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E5%BA%94%E5%BD%93%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="图纸比例为1/2000或1/1000。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA1/2000%E6%88%961/1000%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）修建性详细规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="《编制办法》确定了修建性详细规划的内容：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E3%80%8A%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E4%BA%86%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）建设条件分析及综合技术经济论证；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%8F%8A%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）建筑、道路和绿地等的空间布局和景观规划设计，布置总平面图；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%92%8C%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%80%BB%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3）对住宅、医院、学校和托幼等建筑进行日照分析；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E5%92%8C%E6%89%98%E5%B9%BC%E7%AD%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4）根据交通影响分析，提出交通组织方案和设计方案；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%92%8C%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="5）市政工程管线规划设计和管线综合；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5%EF%BC%89%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E7%AE%A1%E7%BA%BF%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%92%8C%E7%AE%A1%E7%BA%BF%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="6）竖向规划设计；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E6%EF%BC%89%E7%AB%96%E5%90%91%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="7）估算工程量、拆迁量和总造价，分析投资效益。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E7%EF%BC%89%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%87%8F%E3%80%81%E6%8B%86%E8%BF%81%E9%87%8F%E5%92%8C%E6%80%BB%E9%80%A0%E4%BB%B7%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="修建性详细规划文件为规划设计说明书及图纸。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%A6%E5%8F%8A%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="图纸包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="规划范围现状图、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="规划总平面图、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%80%BB%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="各项专业规划图、竖向规划，和反映规划意图的透视效果图等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%81%E7%AB%96%E5%90%91%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%84%8F%E5%9B%BE%E7%9A%84%E9%80%8F%E8%A7%86%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%9B%BE%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="图纸比例一般为1/1000~1/500。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%B8%BA1/1000~1/500%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第三节    城市性质与城市人口" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）城市性质与类型" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E4%B8%8E%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.城市性质的含义" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市性质是指城市在国家经济和社会发展中的地位和作用，在全国城市网络中的分工和职能。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%92%8C%E8%81%8C%E8%83%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市性质体现城市的个性，反映其所在区域的政治、经济、社会、地理、自然等因素的特点。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E5%85%B6%E6%89%80%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%AD%89%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="确定城市性质，是确定城市发展方向和布局的依据，有利于突出规划结构的特点，为规划方案提供可靠的技术经济依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E5%92%8C%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市性质是由城市形成与发展的主导因素的特点所决定，由主要部门职能所体现。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E5%AF%BC%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E6%89%80%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E9%83%A8%E9%97%A8%E8%81%8C%E8%83%BD%E6%89%80%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.城市类型" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="我国城市按职能分为：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%8C%89%E8%81%8C%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="工业城市、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="交通港口城市、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="综合中心城市、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="县城、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8E%BF%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="特殊职能城市。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E8%81%8C%E8%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.城市规模" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市规模是以城市人口规模和用地规模表示城市的大小，通常以城市人口规模来表示。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%92%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E4%BB%A5%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%A5%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="当前，我国城镇化正处于深入发展的关键时期，为了更好地实施人口和城市分类管理，满足经济社会发展需要，将城市规模划分标准调整如表6-1所示：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E5%8C%96%E6%AD%A3%E5%A4%84%E4%BA%8E%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E5%A6%82%E8%A1%A86-1%E6%89%80%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="城市规模划分标准表   6-1   （人口规模以城区常住类型为统计口径）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E8%A1%A8%20%20%206-1%20%20%20%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E4%BB%A5%E5%9F%8E%E5%8C%BA%E5%B8%B8%E4%BD%8F%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%BA%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E5%8F%A3%E5%BE%84%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="小城市：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B0%8F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="Ⅱ型小城市：20万以下的城市" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%85%A1%E5%9E%8B%E5%B0%8F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A20%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="I型小城市：   20万以上50万以下的城市" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3EI%E5%9E%8B%E5%B0%8F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A%20%20%2020%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A50%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text=" 中等城市：50万以上100万以下的城市" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%20%E4%B8%AD%E7%AD%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A50%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A100%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="大城市：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="Ⅱ型大城市：100万以上300万以下的城市" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%85%A1%E5%9E%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A100%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A300%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="I型大城市：300万以上500万以下的城市" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3EI%E5%9E%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A300%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A500%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="特大城市：500万以上1000万以下的城市" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%89%B9%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A500%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A1000%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="超大城市：1000万以上的城市" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%B6%85%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%9A1000%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="注：1.城区是指在市辖区和不设区的市，区、市政府驻地的实际建设连接到的居民委员会所辖区域和其他区域；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%9A1.%E5%9F%8E%E5%8C%BA%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%9C%A8%E5%B8%82%E8%BE%96%E5%8C%BA%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%BE%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A9%BB%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%A7%94%E5%91%98%E4%BC%9A%E6%89%80%E8%BE%96%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="2.常住人口包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%B8%B8%E4%BD%8F%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="居住在本乡镇街道，且户口在本乡镇街道或户口待定的人；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AC%E4%B9%A1%E9%95%87%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%94%E6%88%B7%E5%8F%A3%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AC%E4%B9%A1%E9%95%87%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%E6%88%96%E6%88%B7%E5%8F%A3%E5%BE%85%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="居住在本乡镇街道，且离开户口登记地所在的乡镇街道半年以上的人；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AC%E4%B9%A1%E9%95%87%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%94%E7%A6%BB%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7%E5%8F%A3%E7%99%BB%E8%AE%B0%E5%9C%B0%E6%89%80%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A1%E9%95%87%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="户口在本乡镇街道，且外出不满半年或在境外工作学习的人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%B7%E5%8F%A3%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AC%E4%B9%A1%E9%95%87%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%94%E5%A4%96%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%A1%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%96%E5%9C%A8%E5%A2%83%E5%A4%96%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）城市人口" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.城市人口含义" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）法定城镇地区的常住人口称为城镇人口。城市规划中的城市人口是指市区与近郊区的非农业人口（户籍改革后，尚无明确界定）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%B8%E4%BD%8F%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E3%80%82%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%91%E9%83%8A%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%9E%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%EF%BC%88%E6%88%B7%E7%B1%8D%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%9A%E6%97%A0%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E7%95%8C%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）城市是指国家按行政建制设立的直辖市、市、镇。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E6%8C%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%AE%BE%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B4%E8%BE%96%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%E5%B8%82%E3%80%81%E9%95%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="总人口在2万以下的乡，乡政府驻地非农业人口超过2000人的，或人口在2万人以上的乡，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%80%BB%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%9C%A82%E4%B8%87%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A9%BB%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%9E%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%872000%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%9C%A82%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A1%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="乡政府驻地非农业人口占全乡人口10%以上的，可以设建制镇。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B9%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%A9%BB%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%9E%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%8D%A0%E5%85%A8%E4%B9%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A310%25%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AE%BE%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E9%95%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="少数民族地区、人口稀少的边远地区、山区和示型工矿区、小港口、风景旅游区、边境口岸等地，非农业人口不足2000人的，如确有必要，也可以设置镇的建制。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B0%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%A8%80%E5%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E8%BE%B9%E8%BF%9C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E5%B1%B1%E5%8C%BA%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BA%E5%9E%8B%E5%B7%A5%E7%9F%BF%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E5%B0%8F%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E3%80%81%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E8%BE%B9%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%A3%E5%B2%B8%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%9E%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B32000%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E7%A1%AE%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E9%95%87%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.城市人口构成：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）年龄构成[分托儿（0~3岁、幼儿（4~6岁）、小学（7~11岁）、中学（12~16岁）、成年（17~60岁）、老年（61岁以上）六个组。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%5B%E5%88%86%E6%89%98%E5%84%BF%EF%BC%880~3%E5%B2%81%E3%80%81%E5%B9%BC%E5%84%BF%EF%BC%884~6%E5%B2%81%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A6%EF%BC%887~11%E5%B2%81%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%A6%EF%BC%8812~16%E5%B2%81%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8817~60%E5%B2%81%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E8%80%81%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8861%E5%B2%81%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）性别构成反映男女口之间的数量和比例关系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%A3%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E5%92%8C%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）家庭构成反映城市人口的家庭人口数量、性别、辈分等组合情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E3%80%81%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E3%80%81%E8%BE%88%E5%88%86%E7%AD%89%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）劳动构成在城市总人口中，分为劳动人口和非劳动人口，劳动人口中又分为基本人口和服务人口。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%92%8C%E9%9D%9E%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%88%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）职业构成按行业性质分为12类，按产业类型划分为第一产业、第二产业和第三产业。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E8%81%8C%E4%B8%9A%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E6%8C%89%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA12%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E5%92%8C%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3.城市人口变化的主要表现" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）自然增长。自然增长率 = （本年出生人口数一本年死亡人口数）/年平均人数   × 1000（‰）  （6-1）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E3%80%82%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E7%8E%87%20=%20%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%AC%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%BA%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%AC%E5%B9%B4%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%89/%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%20%20%20%C3%97%201000%EF%BC%88%E2%80%B0%EF%BC%89%20%20%EF%BC%886-1%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）机械增长。机械增长率 = （本年迁入人口—本年迁出人口数）/年平均人数 × 1000（‰）（    6-2）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E3%80%82%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E7%8E%87%20=%20%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%AC%E5%B9%B4%E8%BF%81%E5%85%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E2%80%94%E6%9C%AC%E5%B9%B4%E8%BF%81%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%89/%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%20%C3%97%201000%EF%BC%88%E2%80%B0%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%88%20%20%20%206-2%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）人口平均增长速度。人口平均增长率 = 人口平均发展速度一1   （6-3）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%BF%E7%8E%87%20=%20%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%801%20%20%20%EF%BC%886-3%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4.城市人口规模预测方法" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E9%A2%84%E6%B5%8B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="劳动平衡法、职工带眷系数法和综合平衡法。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E6%B3%95%E3%80%81%E8%81%8C%E5%B7%A5%E5%B8%A6%E7%9C%B7%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%E6%B3%95%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第四节    城市用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E5%9B%9B%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市用地是指用于城市建设和满足城市机能运转所需要的土地，它们既是指已经建设利用的土地，也包括已列入城市建设规划区范围而尚待开发使用的土地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%92%8C%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%BA%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%90%E8%BD%AC%E6%89%80%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E4%BB%AC%E6%97%A2%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%B7%B2%E5%88%97%E5%85%A5%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8C%BA%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E8%80%8C%E5%B0%9A%E5%BE%85%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市的一切建设工程，都必然要落实到土地上，而城市规划的重要工作内容之一是制定城市土地利用规划，通过规划，确定城市用地的规模与范围，以及用地的功能组合与合理利用等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%BD%E5%BF%85%E7%84%B6%E8%A6%81%E8%90%BD%E5%AE%9E%E5%88%B0%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%98%AF%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E4%B8%8E%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E4%B8%8E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市用地具有自然属性、社会属性、经济属性和法律属性，具有使用价值和经济价值，具有行政区划、用途区划和地权区划。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E6%9D%83%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="城市是一个有机的整体，城市的各项机能是相互依存、相互制约的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E6%9C%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E4%BE%9D%E5%AD%98%E3%80%81%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E5%88%B6%E7%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市用地是根据城市机能的需求，按比例、规模合理组合利用的。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="为了科学地制定城市规划，合理利用国土资源，世界各国都对城市用地分类与规划建设用地标准作了规定，对城市（镇）规划编制、管理具有指导作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%86%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9B%BD%E5%9C%9F%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%90%84%E5%9B%BD%E9%83%BD%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E4%BD%9C%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%88%E9%95%87%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%BC%96%E5%88%B6%E3%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E6%8C%87%E5%AF%BC%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="依据《中华人民共和国城乡规划法》，为统筹城乡发展，科学合理地利用土地资源，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E7%BB%9F%E7%AD%B9%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="我国修订发布了《城市用地分类与规划建设用地标准》GB50137-2011，该标准于2012年1月1日开始实施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E4%BF%AE%E8%AE%A2%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E4%BA%86%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%8BGB50137-2011%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%A5%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E4%BA%8E2012%E5%B9%B41%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%AE%9E%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）用地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="用地分类包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城乡用地分类、城市建设用地分类两部分，应按土地使用的主要性质进行划分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E6%8C%89%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.城乡用地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城乡用地共分为2大类、9中类、14小类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%B1%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA2%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%819%E4%B8%AD%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%8114%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2大类的名称、代码和用地内容如表6-2的规定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%A6%82%E8%A1%A86-2%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城乡用地分类（大类）和代码   表6-2" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%88%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%20%20%20%E8%A1%A86-2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="（H） 建设用地：包括城乡居民点建设用地、区域交通设施用地、区域公用设施用地、特殊用地、采矿用地及其他建设用地等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88H%EF%BC%89%20%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%82%B9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E9%87%87%E7%9F%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="（E）非建设用地：水域、农林用地及其他非建设用地等" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88E%EF%BC%89%E9%9D%9E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%9F%E3%80%81%E5%86%9C%E6%9E%97%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%9D%9E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.城市建设用地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市建设用地共分为8大类、35中类、42小类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%B1%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA8%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%8135%E4%B8%AD%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%8142%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="8大类的名称、代码和用地内容如表6-3所列。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E8%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%92%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%A6%82%E8%A1%A86-3%E6%89%80%E5%88%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市建设用地分类（大类）和代码   表6-3" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%88%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%20%20%20%E8%A1%A86-3%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="(R) 居住用地：住宅和相应服务设施的用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E(R)%20%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="(A) 公共管理与公共服务设施用地：行政、文化、教育、体育、卫生等机构和设施的用地，不包括居住用地中的服务设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E(A)%20%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E3%80%81%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E3%80%81%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%AD%89%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E5%92%8C%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="(B) 商业服务业设施用地：商业、商务、娱乐康体等设施用地，不包括居住用地中的服务设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E(B)%20%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A1%E3%80%81%E5%A8%B1%E4%B9%90%E5%BA%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="(M) 工业用地：工矿企业的生产车间、库房及其附属设施用地，包括专用铁路、码头和附属道路、停车场等用地、不包括露天矿用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E(M)%20%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E5%B7%A5%E7%9F%BF%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E8%BD%A6%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%E5%BA%93%E6%88%BF%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%93%E7%94%A8%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E7%A0%81%E5%A4%B4%E5%92%8C%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E5%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%9C%B2%E5%A4%A9%E7%9F%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="(W) 物流仓储用地：物资储备、中转、配送等用地，包括附属道路、停车场以及货运公司车队的站场等用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E(W)%20%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E4%BB%93%E5%82%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E7%89%A9%E8%B5%84%E5%82%A8%E5%A4%87%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%AC%E3%80%81%E9%85%8D%E9%80%81%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E5%9C%BA%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%B4%A7%E8%BF%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%BD%A6%E9%98%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%99%E5%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="(S) 道路与交通设施用地：城市道路、交通设施等用地，不包括居住用地、工业用地等内部的道路、停车场等用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E(S)%20%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E5%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="(U) 公用设施用地：供应、环境、安全等设施用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E(U)%20%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="(G) 绿地与广场用地：公园绿地、防护绿地、广场等公共开放空间用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E(G)%20%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）规划建设用地标准" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.一般规定" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）用地面积应按平面投影计算。每块用地只可计算一次，不得重复。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E5%BA%94%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E6%8A%95%E5%BD%B1%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E3%80%82%E6%AF%8F%E5%9D%97%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%AA%E5%8F%AF%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）城市（镇）总体规划宜采用1/10000或1/5000比例尺的图纸进行建设用地分类计算，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%88%E9%95%87%EF%BC%89%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%AE%9C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A81/10000%E6%88%961/5000%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="控制性详细规划宜采用1/2000或1/1000比例尺的图纸进行用地分类计算。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%AE%9C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A81/2000%E6%88%961/1000%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="现状和规划的用地分类计算应采用同一比例尺。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E5%BA%94%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）用地的计量单位应为万平方米（公顷），代码为“hm2”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A1%E9%87%8F%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%87%E5%B9%B3%E6%96%B9%E7%B1%B3%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AC%E9%A1%B7%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E4%B8%BA%E2%80%9Chm2%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="数字统计精度应根据图纸比例尺确定，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%BA%94%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%B0%BA%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="1/10000图纸应精确至个位，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1/10000%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%B2%BE%E7%A1%AE%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="1/5000图纸应精确至小数点后一位，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1/5000%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%B2%BE%E7%A1%AE%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%8F%E6%95%B0%E7%82%B9%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="1/2000和1/1000图纸应精确至小数点后两位。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1/2000%E5%92%8C1/1000%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%B2%BE%E7%A1%AE%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%8F%E6%95%B0%E7%82%B9%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%A4%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）城市建设用地统计范围与人口统计范围必须一致。、人口规模应按常住人口进行统计。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E3%80%82%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%BA%94%E6%8C%89%E5%B8%B8%E4%BD%8F%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）规划建设用地标准应包括规划人均城市建设用地面积标准、规划人均单项城市建设用地面积标准和规划城市建设用地结构三部分" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%BA%94%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%8D%95%E9%A1%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%89%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.规划人均城市建设用地面积标准" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）规划人均城市建设用地面积指标应根据现状人均城市建设用地面积指标、城市（镇）所在的气候区以及规划人口规模" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E5%BA%94%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%88%E9%95%87%EF%BC%89%E6%89%80%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99%E5%8C%BA%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="按《城市用地分类与规划建设用地标准》表4.2.1人均居住用地面积指标（m2/人）的规定综合确定，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8C%89%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%8B%E8%A1%A84.2.1%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%88m2/%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="并应同时符合表中允许采用的规划人均城市建设用地面积指标和允许调整幅度双因子的限制要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B9%B6%E5%BA%94%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E5%92%8C%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E5%B9%85%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%8C%E5%9B%A0%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）新建城市（镇）的规划人均城市建设用地面积指标宜在85.1~105.0m2/人内确定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%88%E9%95%87%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E5%AE%9C%E5%9C%A885.1~105.0m2/%E4%BA%BA%E5%86%85%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）首都的规划人均城市建设用地面积指标应在105.1~115.0m2/人内确定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E9%A6%96%E9%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E5%BA%94%E5%9C%A8105.1~115.0m2/%E4%BA%BA%E5%86%85%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）边远地区、少数民族地区城市（镇）以及部分山地城市（镇）、人口较少的工矿业城市（镇）、风景旅游城市（镇）等，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E8%BE%B9%E8%BF%9C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B0%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%88%E9%95%87%EF%BC%89%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%B1%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%88%E9%95%87%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E8%BE%83%E5%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%9F%BF%E4%B8%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%88%E9%95%87%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%88%E9%95%87%EF%BC%89%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="不符合规范规定时，应专门论证确定规划人均城市建设用地面积指标，且上限不得大于150.0m2/人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%93%E9%97%A8%E8%AE%BA%E8%AF%81%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%94%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%90%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E150.0m2/%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.规划人均单项城市建设用地面积标准" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%8D%95%E9%A1%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）规划人均居住用地面积指标应符合《城市用地分类与规划建设用地标准》表4.3.1人均居住用地面积指标（m2/人）的规定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E5%BA%94%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%8B%E8%A1%A84.3.1%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%88m2/%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）规划人均公共管理与公共服务设施用地面积不应小于5.5m2/人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E5.5m2/%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）规划人均道路与交通设施用地面积不应小于12.0m2/人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E12.0m2/%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）规划人均绿地与广场用地面积不应小于10.0m2/人，其中人均公园绿地面积不应小于8.0m2/人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E10.0m2/%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E8.0m2/%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4.规划城市建设用地结构" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="居住用地、公共管理与公共服务设施用地、工业用地、道路与交通设施用地和绿地与广场用地五大类主要用地规划占城市建设用地的比例" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8D%A0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="宜符合《城市用地分类与规划建设用地标准》表4.4.1的规定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%9C%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%8B%E8%A1%A84.4.1%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）城市用地条件分析与适用性评价" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%8E%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%84%E4%BB%B7%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市存在于自然环境之中，自然环境是城市规划与建设的条件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.自然条件的分析" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）地质条件" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="表现在城市用地选择和工程建设的工程地质的分析。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%92%8C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）建筑地基。了解建设用地的地基承载力。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%BA%E3%80%82%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%BA%E6%89%BF%E8%BD%BD%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）滑坡与崩塌。确定滑坡地带与稳定用地边界。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E6%BB%91%E5%9D%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%B4%A9%E5%A1%8C%E3%80%82%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E6%BB%91%E5%9D%A1%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%A6%E4%B8%8E%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%BE%B9%E7%95%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3）冲沟。分析冲沟的分布、坡度、活动与否。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E5%86%B2%E6%B2%9F%E3%80%82%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%86%B2%E6%B2%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E3%80%81%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E4%B8%8E%E5%90%A6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4）地震。了解建设区的地震烈度及地质、地形情况和强震区位置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E3%80%82%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E7%83%88%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%8A%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E5%92%8C%E5%BC%BA%E9%9C%87%E5%8C%BA%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="5）矿藏。了解矿藏的分布与开采情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5%EF%BC%89%E7%9F%BF%E8%97%8F%E3%80%82%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E7%9F%BF%E8%97%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E4%B8%8E%E5%BC%80%E9%87%87%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）水文条件及水文地质条件" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B4%E6%96%87%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8A%E6%B0%B4%E6%96%87%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）水文条件。江河湖泊等水体可作城市水源，还对水运交通、改善气候、除污、排雨水、美化环境发挥作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B4%E6%96%87%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%E6%B1%9F%E6%B2%B3%E6%B9%96%E6%B3%8A%E7%AD%89%E6%B0%B4%E4%BD%93%E5%8F%AF%E4%BD%9C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E5%AF%B9%E6%B0%B4%E8%BF%90%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E3%80%81%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99%E3%80%81%E9%99%A4%E6%B1%A1%E3%80%81%E6%8E%92%E9%9B%A8%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%91%E6%8C%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）水文地质。指地下水存在形式、含水层厚度、矿化度？硬度、水温及动态等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B4%E6%96%87%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%82%E6%8C%87%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%B0%B4%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E5%90%AB%E6%B0%B4%E5%B1%82%E5%8E%9A%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E7%9F%BF%E5%8C%96%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%9F%E7%A1%AC%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E6%B8%A9%E5%8F%8A%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）气候条件" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）太阳辐射。是确定建筑的日照标准、间距，朝向及热工设计的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%A4%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%BE%90%E5%B0%84%E3%80%82%E6%98%AF%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%81%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%9D%E5%90%91%E5%8F%8A%E7%83%AD%E5%B7%A5%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）风象。对城市规划与建设的防风、通风、（工程抗风设计和环境保护等有发多方面影响。风象是以风向与风速两个量来表示（图6-5）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E9%A3%8E%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%82%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E9%98%B2%E9%A3%8E%E3%80%81%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E3%80%81%EF%BC%88%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%8A%97%E9%A3%8E%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%AD%89%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%91%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%E9%A3%8E%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E9%A3%8E%E5%90%91%E4%B8%8E%E9%A3%8E%E9%80%9F%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E9%87%8F%E6%9D%A5%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE6-5%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="工业有害气体对下风侧污染系数 = 风向频率 / 平均风速" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%B3%E6%B0%94%E4%BD%93%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%8B%E9%A3%8E%E4%BE%A7%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0%20=%20%E9%A3%8E%E5%90%91%E9%A2%91%E7%8E%87%20/%20%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E9%A3%8E%E9%80%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="为减轻工业对居住的污染影响，因风向不同，其用地布置方式也不同，如图6-6所示。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E5%87%8F%E8%BD%BB%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%AF%B9%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E9%A3%8E%E5%90%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E5%9B%BE6-6%E6%89%80%E7%A4%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3）温度。纬度由赤道向北每增加一度，气温平均降1.5℃。如城市上空出现逆温层或“热岛效应”，在规划布局时，应重视绿化、水面对气温的调节作用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E6%B8%A9%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%E7%BA%AC%E5%BA%A6%E7%94%B1%E8%B5%A4%E9%81%93%E5%90%91%E5%8C%97%E6%AF%8F%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E6%B0%94%E6%B8%A9%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E9%99%8D1.5%E2%84%83%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8A%E7%A9%BA%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E9%80%86%E6%B8%A9%E5%B1%82%E6%88%96%E2%80%9C%E7%83%AD%E5%B2%9B%E6%95%88%E5%BA%94%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E9%87%8D%E8%A7%86%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E9%9D%A2%E5%AF%B9%E6%B0%94%E6%B8%A9%E7%9A%84%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4）降水与湿度。对城市排水和防洪有重大影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E9%99%8D%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8E%E6%B9%BF%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%82%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%92%8C%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）地形条件" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="地形条件对城乡规划与建设的影响如下：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）影响城乡规划布局、平面结构和空间布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%92%8C%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）地面高程和用地间的高差，是用地竖向规划、地面排水和防洪设计的依据。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E9%AB%98%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E5%B7%AE%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%AB%96%E5%90%91%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%92%8C%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3）地面坡度，对规划建设有多方面影响，如表6-4所列。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E8%A1%A86-4%E6%89%80%E5%88%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4）地形与小气候的形成，有利于合理布置建筑。如阳坡建楼，以获得良好日照等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E4%B8%8E%E5%B0%8F%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E9%98%B3%E5%9D%A1%E5%BB%BA%E6%A5%BC%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="5）地貌对通信、电波有一定影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%B0%E8%B2%8C%E5%AF%B9%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E3%80%81%E7%94%B5%E6%B3%A2%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城乡主要建设用地适宜规划坡度表（%）表6-4  （用地名称|最小坡度|最大坡度）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%80%82%E5%AE%9C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%88%25%EF%BC%89%E8%A1%A86-4%20%20%EF%BC%88%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%7C%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8F%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%7C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="工业用地：0.2，10" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A0.2%EF%BC%8C10%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="仓储用地：0.2，10" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%93%E5%82%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A0.2%EF%BC%8C10%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="铁路用地：0，2.0" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A0%EF%BC%8C2.0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="港口用地：0.2，5.0" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A0.2%EF%BC%8C5.0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城镇道路用地：0.2，8.0" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E9%95%87%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A0.2%EF%BC%8C8.0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="居住用地：0.2，25" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A0.2%EF%BC%8C25%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="公共设施用地：0.2，20" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A0.2%EF%BC%8C20%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="城市用地的自然条件评定，通常是将用地分为三类：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%86%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一类用地：是用地自然条件优越，一般不需或只稍加程措施即可用于建设的用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E4%BC%98%E8%B6%8A%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%B8%8D%E9%9C%80%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AA%E7%A8%8D%E5%8A%A0%E7%A8%8B%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="二类用地：是需采取一定工程措施，改善条件后才能修建的用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E9%9C%80%E9%87%87%E5%8F%96%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%90%8E%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="三类用地：是不适于修建的用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%E4%BA%8E%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="注：在山丘地区，一般是按坡度的适用程度划分为10%、10%~25%、&gt;25%三类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%98%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%89%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA10%25%E3%80%8110%25~25%25%E3%80%81&amp;gt;25%25%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="（也有分为0%~8%、8%~15%、15%~25%、&gt;25%四类）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B9%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA0%25~8%25%E3%80%818%25~15%25%E3%80%8115%25~25%25%E3%80%81&amp;gt;25%25%E5%9B%9B%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.城市用地的建设条件分析" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一般所指建设条件是由人为因素所造成的：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%89%80%E6%8C%87%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%BA%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E6%89%80%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）建设现状条件分析内容有三方面：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="1）城市用地布局结构。是指布局结构能否适应发展，对生态环境的影响，与城市内、外交通的关系等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E3%80%82%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E8%83%BD%E5%90%A6%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%86%85%E3%80%81%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="2）城市设施。是指公共服务设施和市政设施现状的质量、数量、容量与利用的潜力等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E3%80%81%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E3%80%81%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%BD%9C%E5%8A%9B%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="3）社会、经济构成。是指人口结构、分布密度、产业结构和就业结构对用地建设的影响。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E3%80%81%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%9A%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%AF%B9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）工程准备条件" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="视自然条件不同而异。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%86%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E8%80%8C%E5%BC%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）基础设施条件" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="含用地本身和邻近地区中可利用的条件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%9C%AC%E8%BA%AB%E5%92%8C%E9%82%BB%E8%BF%91%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第五节    城市的组成要素及规划布局" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在城乡一体化的新时期，城市的组成要素及规划布局分为城乡规划和城市规划两大层面。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%93%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E6%97%B6%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%82%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="一、城乡规划层面" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B1%82%E9%9D%A2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="根据当地自然条件和社会经济发展实际，在保护耕地和生态环境的基础上，将市域内的全部土地规划为建设用地和非建设用地两大类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%80%95%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%9F%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%BA%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E9%9D%9E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="建设用地的组成要素，是由支撑城乡居民生产生活的城乡居民点、区域交通、区域公用设施、特殊用地、采矿和其他六大功能设施用地所构成。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E6%94%AF%E6%92%91%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E9%87%87%E7%9F%BF%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%85%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%89%80%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="其规划布局是根据各项功能特点及技术规范，遵循城乡统筹、合理布局、节约土地、集约发展的原则，在保护自然资源、生态环境和历史文化遗产，防止污染和其他公害，保障公共卫生和公共安全的基础上，科学地做好各项功能用地的规划布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%B5%E5%BE%AA%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%BB%9F%E7%AD%B9%E3%80%81%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%81%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E9%9B%86%E7%BA%A6%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%92%8C%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%B3%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%9C%B0%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="非建设用地规划，是为统筹城乡生产生活，改善城乡生态环境，保护耕地等自然资源，防止污染和其他公害、灾害，科学、合理地划定非建设用地范围。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9D%9E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E7%BB%9F%E7%AD%B9%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%80%95%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%8C%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%B3%E3%80%81%E7%81%BE%E5%AE%B3%EF%BC%8C%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E3%80%81%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%92%E5%AE%9A%E9%9D%9E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="具体组成要素包括水域、农林用地和其他不能建设的空闲地等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%9F%E3%80%81%E5%86%9C%E6%9E%97%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B2%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="二、城市规划层面" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B1%82%E9%9D%A2%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市是由居住、公共管理与公共服务设施、商业服务设施、工业、物流仓储、道路交通设施、公用设施、绿地与广场八类功能要素所组成。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E4%BB%93%E5%82%A8%E3%80%81%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E5%85%AB%E7%B1%BB%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E6%89%80%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）居住用地及规划布局" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="承担居住功能和居住生活的场所称为居住用地，是城市机能的主要组成部分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%89%BF%E6%8B%85%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E7%A7%B0%E4%B8%BA%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.居住用地的内容组成与用地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）用地内容组成" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="居住用地内容组成包括住宅用地和相应服务设施用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）用地分类（参见《城市用地分类与规划建设用地标准》GB50137）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%82%E8%A7%81%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%8BGB50137%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一类居住用地：设施齐全、环境良好、以低层住宅为主；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E7%B1%BB%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E9%BD%90%E5%85%A8%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%82%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="二类居住用地：设施较齐全、环境良好、以多、中、高层住宅为主；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E7%B1%BB%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%BE%83%E9%BD%90%E5%85%A8%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%9A%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%81%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%82%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="三类居住用地：设施、环境较差，以需要加以改造的简陋住宅为主。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%BE%83%E5%B7%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%8A%A0%E4%BB%A5%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E9%99%8B%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.居住用地的选择与分布" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）用地的选择原则" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）有良好的自然条件；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）与工业保持环保距离，靠近就业区；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E7%8E%AF%E4%BF%9D%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3）用地数量与形态要适当集中布置；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8E%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E8%A6%81%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4）依托现有城区，充分利用原有设施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E4%BE%9D%E6%89%98%E7%8E%B0%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）居住用地的分布" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="1）分布方式分集中布置和分散布置两种；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%88%86%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%92%8C%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="2）居住密度分布是根据居住用地分类和集聚效益而定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%86%E8%81%9A%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E8%80%8C%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.居住用地组织与规模" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）居住用地组织原则" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="1）服从总体规划的功能结构和综合效益，内部构成要体现生活的秩序与效能；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%8E%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%88%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="2）用地规模要结合城市道路系统；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="3）配备公共设施要经济合理、方便、安全；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E9%85%8D%E5%A4%87%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="4）符合居民生活行为规律；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%BE%8B%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="5）配合城市行政管理考虑居民组织的适宜规模。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5%EF%BC%89%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%9A%84%E9%80%82%E5%AE%9C%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）居住用地组织方式" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在我国由住宅组团、居住小区、居住区三级构成方式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E7%94%B1%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%A2%E3%80%81%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%B0%8F%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%89%E7%BA%A7%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="4.居住用地指标" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在我国，按新国标规定，城市居住用地占城市建设用地一般为25%~40%，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E6%A0%87%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%A0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%B8%BA25%25~40%25%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="人均指标在I、Ⅱ、I、Ⅶ气候区一般控制在28~38m2/人，在Ⅲ、Ⅳ、V气候区为23~36m2/人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E5%9C%A8I%E3%80%81%E2%85%A1%E3%80%81I%E3%80%81%E2%85%A6%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%9C%A828~38m2/%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E2%85%A2%E3%80%81%E2%85%A3%E3%80%81V%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%BA23~36m2/%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）公共管理与公共服务设施用地及规划布置" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="公共管理与公共服务设施是指政府控制以保障城市基础民生需求的、非盈利的公益性服务设施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%A5%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E3%80%81%E9%9D%9E%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E7%9B%8A%E6%80%A7%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市公共设施的内容和规模，在一定程度上反映了城市生活的质量和水平，其组织与分布直接影响到城市的布局结构。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E4%BA%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.公共管理与公共服务设施用地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="按照《城市用地分类与规划建设用地标准》GB50137的规定，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%8BGB50137%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市公共管理与公共服务设施用地包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="行政办公、文化设施、教育科研、体育、医疗卫生、社会福利、文物古迹、外事、宗教共9中类功能设施用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%A7%91%E7%A0%94%E3%80%81%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%A9%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%A4%E8%BF%B9%E3%80%81%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%81%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E5%85%B19%E4%B8%AD%E7%B1%BB%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）行政办公用地包括：党政机关、社会团体、事业单位等办公机构及相关设施" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%9A%E6%94%BF%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%B3%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%9B%A2%E4%BD%93%E3%80%81%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%9A%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%AD%89%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E5%8F%8A%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）文化设施用地包括：图书、展览等公共文化活动设施用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E3%80%81%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%88%E7%AD%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）教育科研用地包括：高等院校、中等专业学校、中学、小学、科研事业单位及其附属设施用地，包括为学校配建的独立地段的学生生活用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%A7%91%E7%A0%94%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E9%99%A2%E6%A0%A1%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%A6%E3%80%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A6%E3%80%81%E7%A7%91%E7%A0%94%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%9A%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%BA%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E9%85%8D%E5%BB%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）体育用地包括：体育场地和体育训练基地等用地，不包括学校等机构专用的体育设施用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E7%AD%89%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%93%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）医疗卫生用地包括：医疗、保健、卫生、防疫、康复和急救等设施用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E3%80%81%E4%BF%9D%E5%81%A5%E3%80%81%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E3%80%81%E5%BA%B7%E5%A4%8D%E5%92%8C%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（6）社会福利用地包括：为社会提供福利和慈善服务的福利院、养老院、孤儿院等用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BA%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%A9%E5%92%8C%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%A9%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E5%85%BB%E8%80%81%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E5%AD%A4%E5%84%BF%E9%99%A2%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（7）文物古迹用地包括：古遗址、古墓葬、古建筑、石窟寺、近代的代表性建筑、革命纪念建筑等用地，不包括已作其他用途的文物古迹用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%A4%E8%BF%B9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%A4%E9%81%97%E5%9D%80%E3%80%81%E5%8F%A4%E5%A2%93%E8%91%AC%E3%80%81%E5%8F%A4%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E7%9F%B3%E7%AA%9F%E5%AF%BA%E3%80%81%E8%BF%91%E4%BB%A3%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%80%A7%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%B7%B2%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E7%94%A8%E9%80%94%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%A4%E8%BF%B9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（8）外事用地包括：外国驻华使馆、领事馆、国际机构及其生活设施等用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%8B%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%BD%E9%A9%BB%E5%8D%8E%E4%BD%BF%E9%A6%86%E3%80%81%E9%A2%86%E4%BA%8B%E9%A6%86%E3%80%81%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（9）宗教用地系指宗教活动场所用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%889%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%B3%BB%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="依据《城市公共设施规划规范》GB50442-2008的规定，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E3%80%8BGB50442-2008%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市公共设施用地分类应与城市用地分类相对应，分为：行政办公、商业金融、文化娱乐、体育、医疗卫生、教育科研设计和社会福利设施7类用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E3%80%81%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%A8%B1%E4%B9%90%E3%80%81%E4%BD%93%E8%82%B2%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%A7%91%E7%A0%94%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%92%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%A6%8F%E5%88%A9%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD7%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.公共设施用地指标" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市公共管理与公共服务设施用地指标是由城市规模、城市性质、特点，社会、经济发展水平及使用要求所决定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%81%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%89%80%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="根据新国标，此类用地是城市建设用地结构中五大类主要用地之一，其用地占城市建设用地的比例为5%~8%。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A4%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%A0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA5%25~8%25%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="规划人均公共设施用地面积不应小于5.5m2/人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E5.5m2/%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.公共设施的规划布局" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="根据不同性质的公共设施和不同的服务对象，其规划用地宜采用集中与分散相结合的布置方式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%9C%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%8E%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E7%9B%B8%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在城市总体规划阶段。要对全市性和地区性一级的公共设施进行用地分布，组织城市和地区的公共活动中心。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E3%80%82%E8%A6%81%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%A8%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E6%80%A7%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在详细规划阶段，则根据总体规划和地区建设的实际需要，结合规划地区的其他设施内容，对其公共设施用地进行具体布置，以形成居住区级、山区级和不同专业的公共中心。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%B6%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E7%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E5%B1%B1%E5%8C%BA%E7%BA%A7%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="公共设施规划要求如下：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）公共设施项目要合理配置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%A6%81%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）各类公共设施要按照与居民生活的密切程度确定合理的服务半径。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8D%8A%E5%BE%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）公共设施的分布要结合城市交通组织来考虑。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E6%9D%A5%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）根据公共设施本身的特点及其对环境的要求进行布置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E6%9C%AC%E8%BA%AB%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%B9%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）公共设施布置要考虑城市景观组织的要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（6）公共设施的分布要考虑合理的建设时序。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%97%B6%E5%BA%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（7）公共设施的布置要充分利用城市原有基础。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E8%A6%81%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（三）商业服务业设施用地及规划布置" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市商业服务业设施用地（B）是指主要通过市场配置的服务设施，包括政府独立投资或合资建设的设施（如剧院、音乐厅等）用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88B%EF%BC%89%E6%98%AF%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E6%88%96%E5%90%88%E8%B5%84%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%88%E5%A6%82%E5%89%A7%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E5%8E%85%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.商业服务业设施用地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）商业用地，包括零售商业、批发市场、餐饮、旅馆等用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E6%89%B9%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E3%80%81%E9%A4%90%E9%A5%AE%E3%80%81%E6%97%85%E9%A6%86%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）商务用地，包括金融保险、艺术传媒、其他商务（含贸易、设计、咨询等技术服务办公）等用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%A9%E3%80%81%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E4%BC%A0%E5%AA%92%E3%80%81%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%88%E5%90%AB%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E3%80%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E5%92%A8%E8%AF%A2%E7%AD%89%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%EF%BC%89%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）娱乐康体用地，包括娱乐、康体用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%A8%B1%E4%B9%90%E5%BA%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%A8%B1%E4%B9%90%E3%80%81%E5%BA%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）公用设施营业网点用地，包括加油加气站和独立地段的电信、邮政、供水、燃气、供电、供热等营业网点用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%90%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%BD%91%E7%82%B9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9%E5%8A%A0%E6%B0%94%E7%AB%99%E5%92%8C%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%94%B5%E4%BF%A1%E3%80%81%E9%82%AE%E6%94%BF%E3%80%81%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E7%87%83%E6%B0%94%E3%80%81%E4%BE%9B%E7%94%B5%E3%80%81%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E7%AD%89%E8%90%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%BD%91%E7%82%B9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）其他服务设施用地，包括业余学校、民营培训机构、私人诊所、宠物医院、殡葬、汽车修理站等服务设施用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%9A%E4%BD%99%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E3%80%81%E6%B0%91%E8%90%A5%E5%9F%B9%E8%AE%AD%E6%9C%BA%E6%9E%84%E3%80%81%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E8%AF%8A%E6%89%80%E3%80%81%E5%AE%A0%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E3%80%81%E6%AE%A1%E8%91%AC%E3%80%81%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E4%BF%AE%E7%90%86%E7%AB%99%E7%AD%89%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.商业服务业设施用地指标" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="商业服务业设施用地指标是根据城市的性质，规模大小，社会、经济发展水平，以及市民的实际需求而决定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%EF%BC%8C%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E8%80%8C%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="参照《城市公共设施规划规范》GB50442-2008，城市商业设施用地占城市中心城区建设用地的比例应为3.5%~6.5%；人均商业设施用地宜为3.0~6.0m2/人。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%82%E7%85%A7%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E3%80%8BGB50442-2008%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%A0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%9F%8E%E5%8C%BA%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%BA3.5%25~6.5%25%EF%BC%9B%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%9C%E4%B8%BA3.0~6.0m2/%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.商业服务业设施用地的规划布置" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="商业服务业设施用地的规划布置，根据自身的分类特点宜按市级、区级和地区分级设置，形成相应等级和规模的商业服务中心。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%AE%9C%E6%8C%89%E5%B8%82%E7%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BA%E7%BA%A7%E5%92%8C%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E7%BA%A7%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E7%9B%B8%E5%BA%94%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="各级商业服务中心规划用地规模宜为：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%84%E7%BA%A7%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%AE%9C%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="小城市市级中心为30~40公顷；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B0%8F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B8%82%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%BA30~40%E5%85%AC%E9%A1%B7%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="中等城市的市级中心为40~60公顷，区级中心为10~20公顷；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%AD%E7%AD%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%82%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%BA40~60%E5%85%AC%E9%A1%B7%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%BA%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%BA10~20%E5%85%AC%E9%A1%B7%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="大城市的市级中心为60~240公顷，区级中心为20~100公顷；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%82%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%BA60~240%E5%85%AC%E9%A1%B7%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%BA%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%BA20~100%E5%85%AC%E9%A1%B7%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="地区级中心为12~40公顷。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%BA12~40%E5%85%AC%E9%A1%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
      <outline text="市级中心服务人口为50~100万人，服务半径不超过8公里；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B8%82%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%BA50~100%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8D%8A%E5%BE%84%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%878%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="区级中心服务人口为50万人以下，服务半径不超过4公里；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%BA%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%BA50%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8D%8A%E5%BE%84%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%874%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="地区中心服务人口为10万人以下，服务半径不超过1.5公里。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%BA10%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8D%8A%E5%BE%84%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%871.5%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="商业服务业中心规划用地应有良好的交通条件，但不宜沿城市交通干道两侧布置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%89%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E6%B2%BF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%93%E4%B8%A4%E4%BE%A7%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="在历史文化保护城区不宜布置新的大型商服设施用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%9F%8E%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E5%95%86%E6%9C%8D%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="商品批发市场宜根据经营的商品门类选址布局，且不得污染环境。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E6%89%B9%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E5%AE%9C%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%8F%E8%90%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%95%86%E5%93%81%E9%97%A8%E7%B1%BB%E9%80%89%E5%9D%80%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%94%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="商业服务业设施根据与居民生活的密切程度，可按不同门类分别设在居住区内，或远离居住区单独设置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E9%97%A8%E7%B1%BB%E5%88%86%E5%88%AB%E8%AE%BE%E5%9C%A8%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E5%86%85%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E8%BF%9C%E7%A6%BB%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E5%8D%95%E7%8B%AC%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（四）工业用地及规划布局" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="工业是城市形成与发展的主要因素，工业提供大量就业岗位，也带动了其他各项事业的发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8E%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%9A%E5%B2%97%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%B8%A6%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%86%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="工业给城市以生命力，其布置方式也直接影响城市空间布局及城市健康发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%BB%99%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B9%9F%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.城市工业用地及其占地规模" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E5%8D%A0%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）工业用地内容：包括为工矿企业服务的办公室、仓库、食堂等附属设施用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%EF%BC%9A%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%B8%BA%E5%B7%A5%E7%9F%BF%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4%E3%80%81%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E3%80%81%E9%A3%9F%E5%A0%82%E7%AD%89%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）工业用地分类：根据工业对居住和公共环境无干扰、有一定干扰或有严重干扰分为一类工业用地、二类工业用地和三类工业用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%9A%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%AF%B9%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%97%A0%E5%B9%B2%E6%89%B0%E3%80%81%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%B9%B2%E6%89%B0%E6%88%96%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%A5%E9%87%8D%E5%B9%B2%E6%89%B0%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E7%B1%BB%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E4%BA%8C%E7%B1%BB%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）工业占地规模：根据新国标，工业用地应占规划城市建设用地的15%~30%为宜。规划人均工业用地面积指标一般为10~25m2/人之间，最多不大于30m2/人，在特大城市应为18m2/人以下。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8D%A0%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%EF%BC%9A%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%BA%94%E5%8D%A0%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%8415%25~30%25%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%9C%E3%80%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%B8%BA10~25m2/%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E30m2/%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E7%89%B9%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%BA18m2/%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.工业用地规划布局的基本要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）对建设用地要求。工业布局要求用地形状、大小、地形、水源、能源、工程地质、水文地质，要符合工业的具体特点和需求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E7%8A%B6%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E6%96%87%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%92%8C%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）交通运输要求。工业建设与工业生产需要量设备和物资，工业布局与运输方式的关系十分密切。在工业生产中一般采用铁路、水路、公路和连续运输等多种运输方式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%87%8F%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%92%8C%E7%89%A9%E8%B5%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%E3%80%82%E5%9C%A8%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E8%B7%AF%E5%92%8C%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）防止工业对城市环境的污染。工业生产中排出大量废水、废气、废渣和噪声，使空气、水、土壤和环境受到污染。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E3%80%82%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%AD%E6%8E%92%E5%87%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E5%BA%9F%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E5%BA%9F%E6%B0%94%E3%80%81%E5%BA%9F%E6%B8%A3%E5%92%8C%E5%99%AA%E5%A3%B0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%94%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E5%9C%9F%E5%A3%A4%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%97%E5%88%B0%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在规划中工业合理布局，有利于城市环境卫生。减少对城市污染的措施有：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E3%80%82%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="①工业不宜过分集中在一个地段；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A0%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E8%BF%87%E5%88%86%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="②工业布置要综合考虑风向、风速、季节、地形等影响因素；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A1%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E9%A3%8E%E5%90%91%E3%80%81%E9%A3%8E%E9%80%9F%E3%80%81%E5%AD%A3%E8%8A%82%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E7%AD%89%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="③设置必要的防护带；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A2%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E5%B8%A6%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="④对废水、废渣要即时处理、综合利用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E2%91%A3%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%9F%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E5%BA%9F%E6%B8%A3%E8%A6%81%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%B6%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）工业区与居住区的位置。为减少劳动人流上下班的交通消耗，工业区与居住区距离步行应不超过30分钟。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%E4%B8%BA%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E7%8F%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%B6%88%E8%80%97%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%8730%E5%88%86%E9%92%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="当工厂本身过长，工业区与居住区距离过大时应组织公共交通。在规划中，应均衡分布工业区。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BD%93%E5%B7%A5%E5%8E%82%E6%9C%AC%E8%BA%AB%E8%BF%87%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%8C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%A7%E6%97%B6%E5%BA%94%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E3%80%82%E5%9C%A8%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（5）工业区和城市各部分的发展，应保持紧凑集中，互不妨碍，节约用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%BA%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%90%84%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%92%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%A8%E7%A2%8D%EF%BC%8C%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（6）相关企业之间应开展必要的协作、资源的综合利用，减少市内运输。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E5%BA%94%E5%BC%80%E5%B1%95%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%8F%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%81%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%B8%82%E5%86%85%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3.工业在城市中的布局" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="根据工业生产的类别、环境影响、货运量及用地规模，分为布置在远离城区的工业、城市边缘的工业和城市内及居住区内的工业。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%88%AB%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A7%E8%BF%90%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%8A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%9C%A8%E8%BF%9C%E7%A6%BB%E5%9F%8E%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%BE%B9%E7%BC%98%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%86%85%E5%8F%8A%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E5%86%85%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="对各种工业的特点，必须细致分析，才能使布局真正科学合理。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E7%BB%86%E8%87%B4%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%BF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（五）物流仓储用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E4%BB%93%E5%82%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="物流仓储用地是为组织城市生产和生活而设置的物资储备、中转、配送等用地，包括附属道路、停车场及货运公司车队的站场等用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E4%BB%93%E5%82%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%BA%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%92%8C%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%80%8C%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%89%A9%E8%B5%84%E5%82%A8%E5%A4%87%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%BD%AC%E3%80%81%E9%85%8D%E9%80%81%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E5%9C%BA%E5%8F%8A%E8%B4%A7%E8%BF%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%BD%A6%E9%98%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%99%E5%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.物流仓储用地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E4%BB%93%E5%82%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="从对居住和公共环境的影响，可分为三类：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%8E%E5%AF%B9%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%92%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一类用地基本无干扰、污染和安全隐患；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%97%A0%E5%B9%B2%E6%89%B0%E3%80%81%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%9A%90%E6%82%A3%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="二类用地有一定干扰、污染和安全隐患；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%B9%B2%E6%89%B0%E3%80%81%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%9A%90%E6%82%A3%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="三类用地为易燃、易爆和剧毒等危险品的专用物流仓储用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%BA%E6%98%93%E7%87%83%E3%80%81%E6%98%93%E7%88%86%E5%92%8C%E5%89%A7%E6%AF%92%E7%AD%89%E5%8D%B1%E9%99%A9%E5%93%81%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%93%E7%94%A8%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E4%BB%93%E5%82%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.仓库用地布置原则" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）满足仓库用地的技术要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）有利于交通运输。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）有利于建设和经营使用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%8F%E8%90%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）有足够用地和发展余地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E8%B6%B3%E5%A4%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%BD%99%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）沿河布置仓库时，必须留出为居民生活、游憩利用的岸线。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E6%B2%BF%E6%B2%B3%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E7%95%99%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%BA%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E3%80%81%E6%B8%B8%E6%86%A9%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%B2%B8%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（6）注意环保、防止污染、保证城市安全。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E7%8E%AF%E4%BF%9D%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A2%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E3%80%81%E4%BF%9D%E8%AF%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（六）道路与交通设施用地及规划布局" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AD%EF%BC%89%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市道路是连接城市内各项功能用地的纽带，是城市内人流物流的载体，是城市机能的重要组成部分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E6%98%AF%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%86%85%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%BD%E5%B8%A6%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%86%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E7%9A%84%E8%BD%BD%E4%BD%93%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.道路与交通设施用地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="根据新国标，城市道路与交通设施用地分类如下：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）城市道路用地，包括快速路、主干路、次干路、支路及其交叉口用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E4%B8%BB%E5%B9%B2%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E6%AC%A1%E5%B9%B2%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E6%94%AF%E8%B7%AF%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E5%8F%A3%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）城市轨道交通用地，包括独立地段的城市轨道交通地面以上部分的线路、站点用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%BD%A8%E9%81%93%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%BD%A8%E9%81%93%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%BF%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）交通枢纽用地，包括铁路客货运站、公路长途客运站、港口客运码头、公交枢纽及其附属设施用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%9E%A2%E7%BA%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF%E5%AE%A2%E8%B4%A7%E8%BF%90%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E8%B7%AF%E9%95%BF%E9%80%94%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%90%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%90%E7%A0%81%E5%A4%B4%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E4%BA%A4%E6%9E%A2%E7%BA%BD%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）交通场站用地，包括：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%9C%BA%E7%AB%99%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="公共交通场站（含城市轨道交通车辆基地及附属设施，公共汽（电）车首末站、停车场（库）、保养场，出租汽车场站设施等用地，轮渡、缆车、索道等的地面部分及附属设施用地），" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%9C%BA%E7%AB%99%EF%BC%88%E5%90%AB%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%BD%A8%E9%81%93%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BD%A6%E8%BE%86%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E5%8F%8A%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%B1%BD%EF%BC%88%E7%94%B5%EF%BC%89%E8%BD%A6%E9%A6%96%E6%9C%AB%E7%AB%99%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%88%E5%BA%93%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E4%BF%9D%E5%85%BB%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%A7%9F%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E5%9C%BA%E7%AB%99%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E8%BD%AE%E6%B8%A1%E3%80%81%E7%BC%86%E8%BD%A6%E3%80%81%E7%B4%A2%E9%81%93%E7%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%8F%8A%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="以及社会停车场（即独立地段的公共停车场和停车库用地）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%88%E5%8D%B3%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E5%9C%BA%E5%92%8C%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E5%BA%93%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（5）其他交通设施用地，除以上之外的交通设施用地，包括教练场等用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%A4%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%95%99%E7%BB%83%E5%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.城市道路与交通设施用地指标" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="根据新国标，规划人均道路与交通设施用地面积不应小于12m2/人；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BA%BA%E5%9D%87%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E12m2/%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在规划城市建设用地结构中，城市道路与交通设施用地是五大类主要用地之一，其用地占城市规划建设用地的比例为10%~25%。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%A0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%BA10%25~25%25%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.城市道路与交通设施用地规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市道路交通规划必须以总体规划为基础，满足城市功能对交通运输的需求，优化城市用地布局，提高城市的运转效能，提供安全、高效、经济、舒适和低公害的交通条件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%BB%A5%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%90%E8%BD%AC%E6%95%88%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%81%E9%AB%98%E6%95%88%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E8%88%92%E9%80%82%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%B3%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市道路与交通设施规划的具体布局和要求，请参阅《城市道路交通规划设计规范》（GB50220）并将在本章第六节城市总体布局中详述。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%92%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B7%E5%8F%82%E9%98%85%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%88GB50220%EF%BC%89%E5%B9%B6%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AC%E7%AB%A0%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD%E8%8A%82%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%AD%E8%AF%A6%E8%BF%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（七）公用设施" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%83%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市公用设施，是城市供应、环境、安全的基础设施，是城市生产、生活正常运行的保障。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.公用设施分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）供应设施，包括供水、供电、供（燃）气、供热、通信、广播电视等设施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E4%BE%9B%E7%94%B5%E3%80%81%E4%BE%9B%EF%BC%88%E7%87%83%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%94%E3%80%81%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E3%80%81%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E3%80%81%E5%B9%BF%E6%92%AD%E7%94%B5%E8%A7%86%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）环境设施，包括排水、环卫等设施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%8D%AB%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）安全设施，包括消防、防洪等设施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）其他公用设施，除以上之外的公用设施，包括防灾救灾、施工、养护、维修等设施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E9%99%A4%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E9%98%B2%E7%81%BE%E6%95%91%E7%81%BE%E3%80%81%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E3%80%81%E5%85%BB%E6%8A%A4%E3%80%81%E7%BB%B4%E4%BF%AE%E7%AD%89%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.公用设施规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="公用设施规划，根据公用设施的功能性质的分类特点和不同的技术要求，根据国家规范和当地的实际情况做出全面、科学合理的规划。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E5%92%8C%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%81%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="近些年，由于气候、地质变化异常，自然灾害频发，给城市和人民的生命财产造成巨大损失。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%91%E4%BA%9B%E5%B9%B4%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%EF%BC%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%81%BE%E5%AE%B3%E9%A2%91%E5%8F%91%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%99%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E8%B4%A2%E4%BA%A7%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%B7%A8%E5%A4%A7%E6%8D%9F%E5%A4%B1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="加强城市公用设施的规划建设，确保城市安全运行，刻不容缓。城市公用设施规划的具体内容和要求，将在本章第七节中详述。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E4%BF%9D%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E7%BC%93%E3%80%82%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%92%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AC%E7%AB%A0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%83%E8%8A%82%E4%B8%AD%E8%AF%A6%E8%BF%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（八）城市绿地与广场" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AB%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市绿地是以绿色植被为主的城市开放空间，具有调节气候、净化空气、生态美化、避险防灾、卫生隔离、安全防护的功能；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2%E6%A4%8D%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99%E3%80%81%E5%87%80%E5%8C%96%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%94%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E9%81%BF%E9%99%A9%E9%98%B2%E7%81%BE%E3%80%81%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市广场是以游憩、纪念、集会、避险等功能为主的公共活动场地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%86%A9%E3%80%81%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%81%E9%9B%86%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E9%81%BF%E9%99%A9%E7%AD%89%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="绿地与广场是城市公共开放空间用地，是城市机能必不可少的构成要素。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%BF%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E8%A6%81%E7%B4%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.绿地与广场分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）公园绿地（2）防护绿地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）广场等公共开放空间用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%AD%89%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.绿地与广场的用地规模" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="依新国标，城市绿地与广场的用地规模应占规划城市建设用地的10%~15%。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%9D%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%BA%94%E5%8D%A0%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%8410%25~15%25%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.城市绿地与广场规划C" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）城市园林绿地系统规划的具体内容要求、规划布局将在本章第六节中详述。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AC%E7%AB%A0%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD%E8%8A%82%E4%B8%AD%E8%AF%A6%E8%BF%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）城市广场规划，其规划内容和要求，将在本章第十节中详述。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%92%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AC%E7%AB%A0%E7%AC%AC%E5%8D%81%E8%8A%82%E4%B8%AD%E8%AF%A6%E8%BF%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="" _mubu_text="" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="第六节     城市总体布局" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD%E8%8A%82%20%20%20%20%20%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市总体布局是城市的社会、经济、环境及工程技术与建筑空间组合的综合反映，是一项为城市合理发展奠定基础的全局性工作。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%8A%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%A5%A0%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%80%E6%80%A7%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="一、城市用地功能组织" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市总体布局是通过城市用地组成的不同形态体现出来的，其核心是城市用地功能组织。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E6%98%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E5%87%BA%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市功能组织是根据城市的性质、规模，分析城市用地和建设条件，研究各项用地的基本要求，及它们之间的内在联系，安排好位置，处理好它们的关系，有利于城市健康发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%8A%E5%AE%83%E4%BB%AC%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%9C%A8%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%A5%BD%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%A5%BD%E5%AE%83%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="城市用地功能组织可从下面几方面着手：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%8E%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E5%87%A0%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%9D%80%E6%89%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）点、面结合，城乡统一安排" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E9%9D%A2%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市的存在，必须以周围地区的生产发展和需要为前提。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E4%BB%A5%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E5%92%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%BA%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市作为一个点，周围地区作为面，点、面结合，在分析地区工农业生产、地区交通运输、地区水利及矿产资源的综合利用对城市总体布局影响的基础上，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E9%9D%A2%EF%BC%8C%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E9%9D%A2%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E6%B0%B4%E5%88%A9%E5%8F%8A%E7%9F%BF%E4%BA%A7%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="必须把城市与农村、工业与农业、市区与郊区作为一个整体，统一考虑、全面安排、合理制定城市总体布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%8A%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8E%E5%86%9C%E6%9D%91%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%8E%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E5%B8%82%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%8E%E9%83%8A%E5%8C%BA%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E3%80%81%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E3%80%81%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（二）功能明确、重点安排城市主要用地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E3%80%81%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="工业生产是现代城市发展的主要组成。工业布局直接关系到城市的发展规模和方向。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E6%98%AF%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%92%8C%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="综合考虑工业布置与居住生活、交通运输、公共绿地关系，兼顾新、旧区的发展，是城市用地功能组织的重要内容。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%BC%E9%A1%BE%E6%96%B0%E3%80%81%E6%97%A7%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）规划结构清晰、内外交通便捷" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0%E3%80%81%E5%86%85%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%BE%BF%E6%8D%B7%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="结构清晰是反映了城市各主要组成用地功能明确、相互协调，有安全、便捷的交通联系。在规划中应做到以下几点：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E4%BA%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%90%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E3%80%81%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%81%E4%BE%BF%E6%8D%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%E5%9C%A8%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%AD%E5%BA%94%E5%81%9A%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E5%87%A0%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）城市用地各组成部分力求完整、避免穿插。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%90%84%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%8A%9B%E6%B1%82%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E3%80%81%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E7%A9%BF%E6%8F%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）充分考虑各功能分区之间有便捷的交通联系。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%90%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E6%9C%89%E4%BE%BF%E6%8D%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）反对从形式出发，必须因地制宜地探求切合实际的城市用地布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%8D%E5%AF%B9%E4%BB%8E%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%91%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E5%9B%A0%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9C%E5%9C%B0%E6%8E%A2%E6%B1%82%E5%88%87%E5%90%88%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（四）规划建设阶段配合协调、留有发展余地" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E3%80%81%E7%95%99%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%BD%99%E5%9C%B0%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一个城市的形成，需要二三十年。需要不断发展、不断改造、更新、完善、提高。因此制定城市总体布局时，要有一个良好的开端。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%82%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%AD%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E3%80%81%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E3%80%81%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%E3%80%81%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E3%80%82%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E7%AB%AF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）要合理确定第一期建设方案，建设用地力求紧凑、合理、经济、方便。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E8%A6%81%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%9B%E6%B1%82%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E3%80%81%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%81%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）城市建设各阶段要互相衔接、配合协调。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%90%84%E9%98%B6%E6%AE%B5%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%92%E7%9B%B8%E8%A1%94%E6%8E%A5%E3%80%81%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）加强预见性，布局中留有发展余地，规划布局要有“弹性”。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%81%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%AD%E7%95%99%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%BD%99%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E2%80%9C%E5%BC%B9%E6%80%A7%E2%80%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="二、城市总体布局的方案比较" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市总体布局反映城市各项用地的内在联系，综合比较是城市规划设计中的重要工作方法。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%8D%E6%98%A0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%9C%A8%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="因此，城市总体布局需要多作几个不同的规划方案，探求一个经济合理、技术先进的综合方案。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%A0%E6%AD%A4%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%9A%E4%BD%9C%E5%87%A0%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A2%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%85%88%E8%BF%9B%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="在方案比较中，需抓住城市规划建设中的主要矛盾，提出不同的解决办法和措施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E6%8A%93%E4%BD%8F%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="方案比较的内容如下：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）地理位置及工程地质条件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%8A%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）占地、迁居情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%8D%A0%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E8%BF%81%E5%B1%85%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）生产协作情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%8D%8F%E4%BD%9C%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）交通运输情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）环境保护情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（6）居住用地组织情况。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（7）防洪、防震、人防工程措施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%887%EF%BC%89%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E9%9C%87%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E9%98%B2%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（8）市政工程及公用设施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%888%EF%BC%89%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（9）城市总体布局合理。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%889%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（10）城市造价，估算近期建设的总投资。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%8810%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%80%A0%E4%BB%B7%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="上述各点力求文字条理清楚，数据准确明了，图纸形象深刻。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8A%E8%BF%B0%E5%90%84%E7%82%B9%E5%8A%9B%E6%B1%82%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E6%9D%A1%E7%90%86%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%87%86%E7%A1%AE%E6%98%8E%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%BE%E7%BA%B8%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E6%B7%B1%E5%88%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="三、旧城总体布局的调整与完善" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E6%97%A7%E5%9F%8E%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市总体布局是整个城市空间的利用和组合，必须动态地、综合地解决城市问题。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E6%98%AF%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%9C%B0%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="旧城总体布局的调整与完善要做好下列方面工作：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%97%A7%E5%9F%8E%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%97%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）因势利导地利用城市外部的动力，使城市内外部结构协调发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9B%A0%E5%8A%BF%E5%88%A9%E5%AF%BC%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%86%85%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市越现代化，综合效益越高，吸引力越大，影响越远；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%B6%8A%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%95%88%E7%9B%8A%E8%B6%8A%E9%AB%98%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E5%8A%9B%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E8%B6%8A%E8%BF%9C%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市规模越大，城市结构越松散，越要求灵活性，以适应外部社会经济环境条件的变化。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E8%B6%8A%E5%A4%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E8%B6%8A%E6%9D%BE%E6%95%A3%EF%BC%8C%E8%B6%8A%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%81%B5%E6%B4%BB%E6%80%A7%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）充实完善城市基础设施，使城市上下部结构协调发展。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%85%85%E5%AE%9E%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E9%83%A8%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）调整城市用地结构，使城市在发展中取得平衡。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%96%E5%BE%97%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="四、城市道路系统规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市交通分为城市对外交通和城市道路交通两大系统。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%B8%A4%E5%A4%A7%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）城市对外交通" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市对外交通是以城市为基点，与城市外部地域进行交往的各类交通运输的总称，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%9F%9F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%A4%E5%BE%80%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E7%A7%B0%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="它是由铁路、公路、水道、航空、管道等多种运输方式所构成。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%83%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E9%81%93%E3%80%81%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E3%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E9%81%93%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E6%89%80%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市对外交通运输是城市生存和发展的重要条件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="城市对外交通的规划布局和各类交通设施设置的规划原则和技术指标，参照《城市对外交通规划规范》GB50925-2013和《城市道路路线设计规范》CJJ193-2012执行。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%92%8C%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E5%92%8C%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%82%E7%85%A7%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%AF%B9%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E3%80%8BGB50925-2013%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E3%80%8BCJJ193-2012%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）城市道路系统规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.布置城市道路系统的基本要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）在城市用地功能布局的基础上，组织一个完整的道路系统" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E7%9A%84%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市各组成部分是通过城市道路构成一个相互协调、有机联系的整体，道路交通必须满足方便、安全、快速和环境美观的要求，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%90%84%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%98%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E3%80%81%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E8%81%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%81%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%82%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="做到道路功能清楚、系统分明，组成一个合理的交通运输网，主要解决城市内部的客流、货运的流通。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%81%9A%E5%88%B0%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A%E3%80%81%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%88%86%E6%98%8E%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E7%BD%91%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%A2%E6%B5%81%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A7%E8%BF%90%E7%9A%84%E6%B5%81%E9%80%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="道路规划布局要均衡分布，一般干道间距为600~1000m，道路网密度为2~3km/km²。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E8%A6%81%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%93%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E4%B8%BA600~1000m%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%BD%91%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%BA2~3km/km%C2%B2%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）区分不同功能的道路性质" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="按客货流不同、交通工具不同、交通速度差异，将道路区分不同功能为各国所采用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8C%89%E5%AE%A2%E8%B4%A7%E6%B5%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%BA%E5%90%84%E5%9B%BD%E6%89%80%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="我国城市道路规划除大城市设有快速路外，城市道路按四级划分：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%AE%BE%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E8%B7%AF%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E6%8C%89%E5%9B%9B%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%92%E5%88%86%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）快速路" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E8%B7%AF%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="采用中间分隔、全部控制出入、控制出入口间距及形式，实现连续交通流，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E5%88%86%E9%9A%94%E3%80%81%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5%E3%80%81%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E5%8F%8A%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%B5%81%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="具有单向双车道或以上的多车道，并设有配套的交通安全与管理设施的城市道路，红线宽度控制不小于40m。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%95%E5%90%91%E5%8F%8C%E8%BD%A6%E9%81%93%E6%88%96%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E8%BD%A6%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E8%AE%BE%E6%9C%89%E9%85%8D%E5%A5%97%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%8E%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E40m%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2）主干路" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%BB%E5%B9%B2%E8%B7%AF%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在城市道路网中起骨架作用，连接城市各主要分区的交通性干路，红线宽度控制在30~40m。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%BD%91%E4%B8%AD%E8%B5%B7%E9%AA%A8%E6%9E%B6%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%90%84%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%80%A7%E5%B9%B2%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%9C%A830~40m%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3）次干路" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E6%AC%A1%E5%B9%B2%E8%B7%AF%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在城市道路网中起集散交通功能，与主干路结合组成干路网的区域性干路，红线宽度控制在25~40m。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%BD%91%E4%B8%AD%E8%B5%B7%E9%9B%86%E6%95%A3%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%BB%E5%B9%B2%E8%B7%AF%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B2%E8%B7%AF%E7%BD%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E6%80%A7%E5%B9%B2%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%9C%A825~40m%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="4）支路" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E6%94%AF%E8%B7%AF%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="连接次干路与居住区、工业区、交通设施等内部道路，解决局部地区交通，以服务功能为主的道路，红线宽度控制在12~25m。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E6%AC%A1%E5%B9%B2%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%AD%89%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E7%9A%84%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%8C%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%9C%A812~25m%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）充分利用地形、减少工程量" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%81%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%87%8F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在确定道路走向和宽度时，注意节约用地，利用地形尽量减少土方工程量；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E8%B5%B0%E5%90%91%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%9C%9F%E6%96%B9%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="道路选线要绕过地质和水文地质不良地段，路面与地下水保持一定距离，以免冻胀后引起路面开裂。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%89%E7%BA%BF%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E5%92%8C%E6%B0%B4%E6%96%87%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF%E5%9C%B0%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%8C%E8%B7%AF%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8E%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%B0%B4%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%85%8D%E5%86%BB%E8%83%80%E5%90%8E%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E8%B7%AF%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E8%A3%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）要考虑城市环境和城市面貌要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%92%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="道路走向应有利于城市通风，防噪声干扰。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E8%B5%B0%E5%90%91%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%EF%BC%8C%E9%98%B2%E5%99%AA%E5%A3%B0%E5%B9%B2%E6%89%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="可结合道路功能，将城市自然景色、历史文物、现代建筑贯通起来，使城市面貌更加丰富多彩。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%AF%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E6%99%AF%E8%89%B2%E3%80%81%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E3%80%81%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E8%B4%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%E6%9B%B4%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E5%A4%9A%E5%BD%A9%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（5）要满足敷设各种管线及人防工程要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E8%A6%81%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E6%95%B7%E8%AE%BE%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%AE%A1%E7%BA%BF%E5%8F%8A%E4%BA%BA%E9%98%B2%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在确定道路纵断面和路面标高时，要考虑排水管的纵坡度；道路规划以利战备、防灾疏散。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%B5%E6%96%AD%E9%9D%A2%E5%92%8C%E8%B7%AF%E9%9D%A2%E6%A0%87%E9%AB%98%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%B5%E5%9D%A1%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%9B%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%BB%A5%E5%88%A9%E6%88%98%E5%A4%87%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E7%81%BE%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.城市道路系统及道路宽度的确定" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%8F%8A%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）城市道路的形式与功能" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8E%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市道路系统一般归纳为方格棋盘式、环形放射式和自由式几种。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%A0%BC%E6%A3%8B%E7%9B%98%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%BD%A2%E6%94%BE%E5%B0%84%E5%BC%8F%E5%92%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E5%BC%8F%E5%87%A0%E7%A7%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="这是根据当地的社会、自然和现状条件所确定，按道路系统的基本要求进行合理布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%81%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%89%80%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%89%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="按道路的功能特点和两旁的建筑分布来组成不同的城市道路系统。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8C%89%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%A4%E6%97%81%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E6%9D%A5%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="如桂林是风景城市，城市道路按它的服务功能分为生活性道路、交通性道路、游览性道路三类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E6%A1%82%E6%9E%97%E6%98%AF%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E6%8C%89%E5%AE%83%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%80%A7%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%80%A7%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E6%B8%B8%E8%A7%88%E6%80%A7%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%89%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）完善道路系统的措施" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="通常采用快、慢车分流，客、货分流，过境与市内交通分流，机动车与非机动车分流；开辟步行区、自行车道、快速公共交通专用道等措施。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%9A%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E5%BF%AB%E3%80%81%E6%85%A2%E8%BD%A6%E5%88%86%E6%B5%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%A2%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A7%E5%88%86%E6%B5%81%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%87%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%86%85%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%88%86%E6%B5%81%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%BA%E5%8A%A8%E8%BD%A6%E4%B8%8E%E9%9D%9E%E6%9C%BA%E5%8A%A8%E8%BD%A6%E5%88%86%E6%B5%81%EF%BC%9B%E5%BC%80%E8%BE%9F%E6%AD%A5%E8%A1%8C%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%81%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E8%BD%A6%E9%81%93%E3%80%81%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E4%B8%93%E7%94%A8%E9%81%93%E7%AD%89%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）旧城道路系统的改善" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%97%A7%E5%9F%8E%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="1）对原有道路作必要的分工，重新分配车流和人流；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%AF%B9%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%89%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%BD%9C%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E8%BD%A6%E6%B5%81%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="2）利用平行街道，开辟单向行车；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%8C%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%80%E8%BE%9F%E5%8D%95%E5%90%91%E8%A1%8C%E8%BD%A6%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="3）修建环行干道，减轻原有道路的交通负担；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E4%BF%AE%E5%BB%BA%E7%8E%AF%E8%A1%8C%E5%B9%B2%E9%81%93%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%8F%E8%BD%BB%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%89%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%B4%9F%E6%8B%85%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="4）封闭次要交叉口，加大主交叉口间距。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E5%B0%81%E9%97%AD%E6%AC%A1%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E5%8F%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E5%8F%A3%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）道路宽度及断面组合的确定" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%8A%E6%96%AD%E9%9D%A2%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="确定道路红线宽度应根据城市性质、规模和道路系统规划的要求，考虑交通量（机动车、非机动车、人行交通）、日照通风、管线敷设及建筑布置等因素。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E5%BA%94%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%92%8C%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%BA%E5%8A%A8%E8%BD%A6%E3%80%81%E9%9D%9E%E6%9C%BA%E5%8A%A8%E8%BD%A6%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E6%97%A5%E7%85%A7%E9%80%9A%E9%A3%8E%E3%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%BA%BF%E6%95%B7%E8%AE%BE%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E7%AD%89%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="道路红线宽度是道路、市政横断面中各种用地宽度的总和，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E6%98%AF%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E6%A8%AA%E6%96%AD%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%AD%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E5%92%8C%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="其中机动车道占主要部分。一条车道宽度为3.5m，一条快车道宽为3.75~4m，所需车道数视具体情况而定。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%B6%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%BA%E5%8A%A8%E8%BD%A6%E9%81%93%E5%8D%A0%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%A1%E8%BD%A6%E9%81%93%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%BA3.5m%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%A1%E5%BF%AB%E8%BD%A6%E9%81%93%E5%AE%BD%E4%B8%BA3.75~4m%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E9%9C%80%E8%BD%A6%E9%81%93%E6%95%B0%E8%A7%86%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E8%80%8C%E5%AE%9A%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="道路横断面的基本形式有一块板（红线宽40m以下）、两块板、三块板（红线宽40m以上）三种。形式确定应因地制宜（图6-7）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E6%A8%AA%E6%96%AD%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%9D%97%E6%9D%BF%EF%BC%88%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%BD40m%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E4%B8%A4%E5%9D%97%E6%9D%BF%E3%80%81%E4%B8%89%E5%9D%97%E6%9D%BF%EF%BC%88%E7%BA%A2%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%BD40m%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%89%E7%A7%8D%E3%80%82%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%BA%94%E5%9B%A0%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9C%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE6-7%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.城市交通运输组织" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市交通运输的合理组织，应使客运、货运的交通量在城市中均衡分布、减少彼此干扰；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E7%9A%84%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E4%BD%BF%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%90%E3%80%81%E8%B4%A7%E8%BF%90%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E9%87%8F%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E3%80%81%E5%87%8F%E5%B0%91%E5%BD%BC%E6%AD%A4%E5%B9%B2%E6%89%B0%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="合理布置主要吸引人流的公共建筑物；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%B5%81%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E7%89%A9%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="引开过境交通，合理布置大型停车场；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BC%95%E5%BC%80%E8%BF%87%E5%A2%83%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E5%81%9C%E8%BD%A6%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="组成地上、地下结合的交通枢纽。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E6%9E%A2%E7%BA%BD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="五、城市绿地系统规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%94%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市绿地系统规划的任务是：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="制定城市各类绿地的用地指标，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="选定各项绿地的用地范围，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%80%89%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="合理安排整个城市的绿地布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（一）城市绿地的功能" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）保护环境：防风沙、保水土、净化空气、降低噪声。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%9A%E9%98%B2%E9%A3%8E%E6%B2%99%E3%80%81%E4%BF%9D%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%9F%E3%80%81%E5%87%80%E5%8C%96%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%94%E3%80%81%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E5%99%AA%E5%A3%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）改善城市面貌、提供休息游览场所。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%E3%80%81%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%BC%91%E6%81%AF%E6%B8%B8%E8%A7%88%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）有利于战备、防震、抗灾。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%98%E5%A4%87%E3%80%81%E9%98%B2%E9%9C%87%E3%80%81%E6%8A%97%E7%81%BE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）城市绿地分类" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="绿地应按主要功能进行分类，并可分为大类、中类、小类三个层次。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E5%BA%94%E6%8C%89%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%81%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E5%B1%82%E6%AC%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）公园绿地（G1）：向公众开放，以游戏为主要功能，兼具生态、景观、文教和应急避险等功能，有一定游憩和服务设施的绿地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88G1%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E5%90%91%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%BC%E5%85%B7%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E3%80%81%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E3%80%81%E6%96%87%E6%95%99%E5%92%8C%E5%BA%94%E6%80%A5%E9%81%BF%E9%99%A9%E7%AD%89%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%B8%B8%E6%86%A9%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="此大类下设综合公园（G11）、社区公园（G12）、专类公园（G13）、游园（G14）4个中类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%88G11%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E5%8C%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%88G12%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E4%B8%93%E7%B1%BB%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%88G13%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E6%B8%B8%E5%9B%AD%EF%BC%88G14%EF%BC%894%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%AD%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）防护绿地（G2）：用地独立，具有卫生、隔离、安全、生态防护功能，游人不宜进入的绿地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88G2%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%B8%B8%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%9C%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="主要包括卫生隔离防护绿地、道路及铁路防护绿地、高压走廊防护绿地、公用设施防护绿地等。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%8F%8A%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E9%AB%98%E5%8E%8B%E8%B5%B0%E5%BB%8A%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）广场绿地（G3）：以游憩、纪念、集会和避险等功能为主的城市公共活动场地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88G3%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%86%A9%E3%80%81%E7%BA%AA%E5%BF%B5%E3%80%81%E9%9B%86%E4%BC%9A%E5%92%8C%E9%81%BF%E9%99%A9%E7%AD%89%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%9C%BA%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="绿化占地比例宜大于或等于35%；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E5%8D%A0%E5%9C%B0%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%AE%9C%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%96%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E35%25%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="绿化占地比例大于或筹于65%的广场用地计入公园绿地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E5%8D%A0%E5%9C%B0%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%96%E7%AD%B9%E4%BA%8E65%25%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E8%AE%A1%E5%85%A5%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）附属绿地（XG）：附属于各类建设用地（除“绿地与广场用地”）的绿化用地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88XG%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%99%84%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E5%90%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88%E9%99%A4%E2%80%9C%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8E%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="包括居住用地、公共管理与公共服务设施用地、商业服务业设施用地、工业用地、物流仓储用地、道路与交通设施用地、公用设施用地等用地中的绿地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E4%BB%93%E5%82%A8%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E7%AD%89%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="不再重复参与城市建设用地平衡。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（5）区域绿地（EG）：位于城市建设用地之外，具有城乡生态环境及自然资源和文化资源保护、游憩健身、园林苗术生产等功能的绿地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88EG%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E6%9C%89%E5%9F%8E%E4%B9%A1%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%8A%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E5%92%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E3%80%81%E6%B8%B8%E6%86%A9%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E3%80%81%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E8%8B%97%E6%9C%AF%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%AD%89%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="不参与建设用地汇总，不包括耕地。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%B1%87%E6%80%BB%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E8%80%95%E5%9C%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="此大类下设风景游憩绿地（EG1）、生态保育绿地（EG2）、区域设施防护绿地（EG3）、生产绿地（EG4）4个中类。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E6%B8%B8%E6%86%A9%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88EG1%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81%E4%BF%9D%E8%82%B2%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88EG2%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88EG3%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%88EG4%EF%BC%894%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%AD%E7%B1%BB%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="注：依据《城市绿地分类标准》CJJ/T85-2017。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%9A%E4%BE%9D%E6%8D%AE%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E3%80%8BCJJ/T85-2017%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（三）城市绿地的规划布置" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）均衡分布，连成完整的园林绿地系统，做到点、线、面相结合。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%9D%87%E8%A1%A1%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9E%E6%88%90%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%AD%E6%9E%97%E7%BB%BF%E5%9C%B0%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%81%9A%E5%88%B0%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%81%E9%9D%A2%E7%9B%B8%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）因地制宜，与河湖山川自然环境相结合。其布置形式有块状、带状、楔形、环形或穿插分布。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%9B%A0%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9C%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8E%E6%B2%B3%E6%B9%96%E5%B1%B1%E5%B7%9D%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9B%B8%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E3%80%82%E5%85%B6%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%9C%89%E5%9D%97%E7%8A%B6%E3%80%81%E5%B8%A6%E7%8A%B6%E3%80%81%E6%A5%94%E5%BD%A2%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%96%E7%A9%BF%E6%8F%92%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="六、城市总体艺术布局" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%85%AD%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（一）城市总体艺术布局要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.城市总体艺术布局与城市规划的关系" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一个城市规划，不仅要创造良好的生产、生活环境，而且应有优美的城市景观。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%85%E8%A6%81%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E3%80%81%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%89%E4%BC%98%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市总体艺术布局，是根据城市的性质、规模、现状条件、城市用地总体规划，形成城市建设艺术布局的基本构思，确定城市建设艺术骨架。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%81%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%9E%84%E6%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%AA%A8%E6%9E%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="在详细规划中，要根据总体规划的艺术布局，进行城市空间组合，以达到城市建设艺术的整体与局部的协调统一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%A5%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="2.城市总体艺术布局与城市面貌的关系" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市艺术布局，要体现城市美学要求，为城市环境中自然美与人工美的综合，" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%B8%AD%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="如建筑、道路、桥梁的布置与山势、水面、林木的良好结合；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E3%80%81%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%81%E6%A1%A5%E6%A2%81%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%B1%E5%8A%BF%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%81%E6%9E%97%E6%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市艺术面貌，是自然与人工、空间与时间、静态与动态的相互结合、交替变化而构成。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E3%80%81%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E3%80%81%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E4%B8%8E%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B8%E4%BA%92%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E3%80%81%E4%BA%A4%E6%9B%BF%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E8%80%8C%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.城市总体艺术布局的协调统一要求" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%8F%E8%B0%83%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）艺术布局与适用、经济的统一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8E%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E3%80%81%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）近期艺术面貌与远期艺术面貌的统一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%9C%E6%9C%9F%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）整体与局部、重点与非重点的统一。要点、线、面相结合。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8E%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E3%80%81%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E4%B8%8E%E9%9D%9E%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%E8%A6%81%E7%82%B9%E3%80%81%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%81%E9%9D%A2%E7%9B%B8%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（4）历史条件、时代精神、不同风格、不同处理手法的统一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%81%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E3%80%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E6%89%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（5）艺术布局与施工技术条件的统一。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B8%8E%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4.城市艺术面貌与环境保护、公用设施、城市管理密不可分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%E4%B8%8E%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E3%80%81%E5%85%AC%E7%94%A8%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%AF%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）自然环境、历史条件、工程设施与城市艺术布局关系密切" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E3%80%81%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%81%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E4%B8%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%AF%86%E5%88%87%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1.自然环境的利用" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%9A%84%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）平原地区，规划布局紧凑整齐。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E5%B9%B3%E5%8E%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E7%B4%A7%E5%87%91%E6%95%B4%E9%BD%90%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="为避免城市艺术布局单调，有时采用挖低补高、堆山积水、加强绿化、建筑高低配置得当，道路广场、" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BA%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E5%8D%95%E8%B0%83%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%97%B6%E9%87%87%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%96%E4%BD%8E%E8%A1%A5%E9%AB%98%E3%80%81%E5%A0%86%E5%B1%B1%E7%A7%AF%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%BA%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8E%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%BE%97%E5%BD%93%EF%BC%8C%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E5%B9%BF%E5%9C%BA%E3%80%81%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="主景对景的尺度处理适宜的手段，给城市创造丰富而有变化的立体空间。如北京。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E6%99%AF%E5%AF%B9%E6%99%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%BA%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E9%80%82%E5%AE%9C%E7%9A%84%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%99%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E8%80%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%98%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E7%AB%8B%E4%BD%93%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）丘陵山川地区的城市规划布局，应充分结合地形条件。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%98%E9%99%B5%E5%B1%B1%E5%B7%9D%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="如兰州位于黄河河谷地带，采取分散与集中相结合的布局，城市分为四个相对独立的地区；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E5%85%B0%E5%B7%9E%E4%BD%8D%E4%BA%8E%E9%BB%84%E6%B2%B3%E6%B2%B3%E8%B0%B7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%A6%EF%BC%8C%E9%87%87%E5%8F%96%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E4%B8%8E%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%9B%B8%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%AA%E7%9B%B8%E5%AF%B9%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="拉萨建筑依山建设、层层叠叠，主体空间感较强。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8B%89%E8%90%A8%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E4%BE%9D%E5%B1%B1%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E3%80%81%E5%B1%82%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%A0%E5%8F%A0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E4%BD%93%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E6%84%9F%E8%BE%83%E5%BC%BA%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）滨临河湖水域的城市，应充分利用水域进行城市艺术布局。如杭州、苏州、威尼斯等城市。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%BB%A8%E4%B8%B4%E6%B2%B3%E6%B9%96%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%85%85%E5%88%86%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%9F%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%E5%A6%82%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7%9E%E3%80%81%E8%8B%8F%E5%B7%9E%E3%80%81%E5%A8%81%E5%B0%BC%E6%96%AF%E7%AD%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.历史条件的利用" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="对历史遗留下来的文化遗产和艺术面貌、要分别情况进行保留、改造、迁移、拆除、恢复等多种方式的处理。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AF%B9%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E9%81%97%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7%E5%92%8C%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%E3%80%81%E8%A6%81%E5%88%86%E5%88%AB%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%9D%E7%95%99%E3%80%81%E6%94%B9%E9%80%A0%E3%80%81%E8%BF%81%E7%A7%BB%E3%80%81%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4%E3%80%81%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D%E7%AD%89%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.结合城市工程设施、组织城市艺术面貌" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%E3%80%81%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="结合城市的防洪、排涝、蓄水、护坡、护堤等工程设施，进行城市艺术面貌的处理。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E9%98%B2%E6%B4%AA%E3%80%81%E6%8E%92%E6%B6%9D%E3%80%81%E8%93%84%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E6%8A%A4%E5%9D%A1%E3%80%81%E6%8A%A4%E5%A0%A4%E7%AD%89%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%AE%BE%E6%96%BD%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%9D%A2%E8%B2%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="如北京的陶然亭公园、天津的水上公园的形成就是良好的范例。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%9A%84%E9%99%B6%E7%84%B6%E4%BA%AD%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E3%80%81%E5%A4%A9%E6%B4%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%8C%83%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="建筑是景观的重要组成部分，在完成景观规划设计后再进行工程施工，更能确保景观设计质量。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E6%98%AF%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E7%9A%84%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%B4%E8%83%BD%E7%A1%AE%E4%BF%9D%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%B4%A8%E9%87%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）城市景观设计" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市景观是城市形态特征给人们带来的视觉感受，是城市艺术的具体表现形式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E7%BB%99%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%AC%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%97%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="一个优美的城市景观和优秀的环境艺术，是一个城市文明进步的象征和精神风貌的具体体现。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%BC%98%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E5%92%8C%E4%BC%98%E7%A7%80%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E8%BF%9B%E6%AD%A5%E7%9A%84%E8%B1%A1%E5%BE%81%E5%92%8C%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E9%A3%8E%E8%B2%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E4%BD%93%E7%8E%B0%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="城市景观设计是根据城市的性质规模、社会文化、地形地貌、河湖水系、名胜古迹、林木绿化、有价值的建筑及可利用的优美景物，经研究分析后，通过艺术手段的再创造，将其组织到城市的总体艺术布局之中。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%98%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E5%9C%B0%E8%B2%8C%E3%80%81%E6%B2%B3%E6%B9%96%E6%B0%B4%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%81%E5%90%8D%E8%83%9C%E5%8F%A4%E8%BF%B9%E3%80%81%E6%9E%97%E6%9C%A8%E7%BB%BF%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%91%E5%8F%8A%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%98%E7%BE%8E%E6%99%AF%E7%89%A9%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%8F%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E6%89%8B%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%86%8D%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%85%B6%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E5%88%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="例如利用地形可创造优美的山城、水城、平原型等不同特征的城市景观；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%A2%E5%8F%AF%E5%88%9B%E9%80%A0%E4%BC%98%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%B1%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%81%E5%B9%B3%E5%8E%9F%E5%9E%8B%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%99%AF%E8%A7%82%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
