    <outline text="给水工程分为取水工程、净水工程和输配水工程三部分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E7%BB%99%E6%B0%B4%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%8F%96%E6%B0%B4%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E3%80%81%E5%87%80%E6%B0%B4%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%92%8C%E8%BE%93%E9%85%8D%E6%B0%B4%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%89%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）水源选择的原则" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）水源水量必须充沛，保证枯水期供水充足；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E6%B0%B4%E9%87%8F%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E5%85%85%E6%B2%9B%EF%BC%8C%E4%BF%9D%E8%AF%81%E6%9E%AF%E6%B0%B4%E6%9C%9F%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4%E5%85%85%E8%B6%B3%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）取用良好水质的水源；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%96%E7%94%A8%E8%89%AF%E5%A5%BD%E6%B0%B4%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3）根据城市布局，可选一个或几个水源，或集中供水或分散供水，或二者结合；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%88%96%E5%87%A0%E4%B8%AA%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4%E6%88%96%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%96%E4%BA%8C%E8%80%85%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4）选择水源要考虑当前、近期和远期对水量、水质的要求；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E3%80%81%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%92%8C%E8%BF%9C%E6%9C%9F%E5%AF%B9%E6%B0%B4%E9%87%8F%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E8%B4%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="5）选择水源，要考虑吸水、输水方便，施工、运输、管理、维护的安全经济。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5%EF%BC%89%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E5%90%B8%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E8%BE%93%E6%B0%B4%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%BF%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E3%80%81%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E3%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E3%80%81%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%BB%8F%E6%B5%8E%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）水源的卫生防护" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="在水源周围建立的卫生防护地带分为：警戒区和限制区（图6-8）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9C%A8%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%B4%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%98%B2%E6%8A%A4%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%A6%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%AD%A6%E6%88%92%E5%8C%BA%E5%92%8C%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%8C%BA%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE6-8%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）水厂的选址要求C水厂用地，宜选在接近用水区。井群应布置在城市上游，井管之间要保持一定间距。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E6%B0%B4%E5%8E%82%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E5%9D%80%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82C%E6%B0%B4%E5%8E%82%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9C%E9%80%89%E5%9C%A8%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E7%94%A8%E6%B0%B4%E5%8C%BA%E3%80%82%E4%BA%95%E7%BE%A4%E5%BA%94%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8A%E6%B8%B8%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%95%E7%AE%A1%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E8%A6%81%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3.给水管网规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E7%BB%99%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E7%BD%91%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市用水是通过输水干管和敷设配水管网送到用户的，输水管不少于两条。管网布置有树枝状和环状两种形式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%A8%E6%B0%B4%E6%98%AF%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E8%BE%93%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B2%E7%AE%A1%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B7%E8%AE%BE%E9%85%8D%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E7%BD%91%E9%80%81%E5%88%B0%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E8%BE%93%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%A4%E6%9D%A1%E3%80%82%E7%AE%A1%E7%BD%91%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E6%9C%89%E6%A0%91%E6%9E%9D%E7%8A%B6%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%AF%E7%8A%B6%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（二）城市排水工程规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="排水工程：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
        <outline text="一是把污水、废水集中并送到适当地点进行处理，达到卫生要求后再排放到水体中；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%8A%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%81%E5%BA%9F%E6%B0%B4%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B6%E9%80%81%E5%88%B0%E9%80%82%E5%BD%93%E5%9C%B0%E7%82%B9%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E8%BE%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E6%8E%92%E6%94%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%B0%B4%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="二是把雨水及时排除；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BA%8C%E6%98%AF%E6%8A%8A%E9%9B%A8%E6%B0%B4%E5%8F%8A%E6%97%B6%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
        <outline text="三是污水的综合利用。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%89%E6%98%AF%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      </outline>
    </outline>
    <outline text="1.城市排水量的估算" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1.%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（1）生活污水量，可参考表6-6。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E8%A1%A86-6%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="居住区生活污水量表6-6   （平均日污水量[L/（人·d）]）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E9%87%8F%E8%A1%A86-6%20%20%20%EF%BC%88%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%97%A5%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E9%87%8F%5BL/%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%BA%C2%B7d%EF%BC%89%5D%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="室内卫生设备情况：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="室内无给水排水卫生设备，从集中给水龙头取水，由室外排水管道排水：10~40" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E6%97%A0%E7%BB%99%E6%B0%B4%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%BB%99%E6%B0%B4%E9%BE%99%E5%A4%B4%E5%8F%96%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E5%AE%A4%E5%A4%96%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E9%81%93%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%9A10~40%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="室内有给水排水设备，但无水冲式厕所：20~70" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%99%E6%B0%B4%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%97%A0%E6%B0%B4%E5%86%B2%E5%BC%8F%E5%8E%95%E6%89%80%EF%BC%9A20~70%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="室内有给水排水卫生设备，但无淋浴设备：55~100" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%99%E6%B0%B4%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%97%A0%E6%B7%8B%E6%B5%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%9A55~100%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="室内有给排水卫生设备和淋浴设备：90~160" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%99%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%92%8C%E6%B7%8B%E6%B5%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%9A90~160%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="室内有给水排水卫生设备，并有淋浴和集中热水供应：130~190" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%AE%A4%E5%86%85%E6%9C%89%E7%BB%99%E6%B0%B4%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E6%9C%89%E6%B7%8B%E6%B5%B4%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%83%AD%E6%B0%B4%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%EF%BC%9A130~190%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（2）工业废水量包括生产污水和生产废水两种，由工厂提供数值。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E5%BA%9F%E6%B0%B4%E9%87%8F%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E5%92%8C%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E5%BA%9F%E6%B0%B4%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B1%E5%B7%A5%E5%8E%82%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）雨水量，根据降雨强度和汇水面积计算。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E9%9B%A8%E6%B0%B4%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%8C%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E9%99%8D%E9%9B%A8%E5%BC%BA%E5%BA%A6%E5%92%8C%E6%B1%87%E6%B0%B4%E9%9D%A2%E7%A7%AF%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2.排水工程的组成和排水系统" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2.%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="排水工程包括排水管道和污水处理厂两部分。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E9%81%93%E5%92%8C%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%8E%82%E4%B8%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）排水制度有分流制和合流制两种。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%88%86%E6%B5%81%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%90%88%E6%B5%81%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）排水系统的几种布置形式（图6-9）：" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E6%8E%92%E6%B0%B4%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%87%A0%E7%A7%8D%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%BE6-9%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9A%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="1）截流布置；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E6%88%AA%E6%B5%81%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="2）扇形布置；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E6%89%87%E5%BD%A2%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="3）分区布置；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="4）分散布置。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E5%B8%83%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="3.污水处理厂的用地选择" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3.%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%8E%82%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="污水处理厂应设在城市水体的下游、地势较低、便于城市污水汇流入厂内，远离居住区之处。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%8E%82%E5%BA%94%E8%AE%BE%E5%9C%A8%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%B4%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8B%E6%B8%B8%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%BF%E8%BE%83%E4%BD%8E%E3%80%81%E4%BE%BF%E4%BA%8E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E6%B1%87%E6%B5%81%E5%85%A5%E5%8E%82%E5%86%85%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9C%E7%A6%BB%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E5%8C%BA%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%84%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（三）城市电力系统规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="城市电力系统规划，一般以区域的动力资源供电系统规划为基础，要调查收集城市电源、电力网、电力负荷等级现状资料，分析发展的可能，对城市供电做出综合安排。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%BB%A5%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%94%B5%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E4%B8%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%81%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%B5%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E7%BD%91%E3%80%81%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E8%B4%9F%E8%8D%B7%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E7%8E%B0%E7%8A%B6%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BE%9B%E7%94%B5%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="城市电力系统主要解决电力负荷及电力平衡，城市供电电源和供电系统及其布局。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E8%B4%9F%E8%8D%B7%E5%8F%8A%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BE%9B%E7%94%B5%E7%94%B5%E6%BA%90%E5%92%8C%E4%BE%9B%E7%94%B5%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（1）电力系统规划的内容" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="1）城市电源的选择；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E1%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%94%B5%E6%BA%90%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="2）分期负荷及电力平衡；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E2%EF%BC%89%E5%88%86%E6%9C%9F%E8%B4%9F%E8%8D%B7%E5%8F%8A%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="3）发电厂、变电所、配电所的位置、容量及数量；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E3%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%91%E7%94%B5%E5%8E%82%E3%80%81%E5%8F%98%E7%94%B5%E6%89%80%E3%80%81%E9%85%8D%E7%94%B5%E6%89%80%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%81%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%8A%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="4）电压等级的确定；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E4%EF%BC%89%E7%94%B5%E5%8E%8B%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="5）确定高压线走向、高压走廊的位置、低压接线的方式；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E5%EF%BC%89%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E9%AB%98%E5%8E%8B%E7%BA%BF%E8%B5%B0%E5%90%91%E3%80%81%E9%AB%98%E5%8E%8B%E8%B5%B0%E5%BB%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%81%E4%BD%8E%E5%8E%8B%E6%8E%A5%E7%BA%BF%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="6）电力负荷分布图；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E6%EF%BC%89%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E8%B4%9F%E8%8D%B7%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%9B%BE%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="7）电力系统供电的总平面图。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E7%EF%BC%89%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%BE%9B%E7%94%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%80%BB%E5%B9%B3%E9%9D%A2%E5%9B%BE%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（2）电力负荷的分布" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E8%B4%9F%E8%8D%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="一般分为工业、农业、市政及生活用户。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E5%88%86%E4%B8%BA%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E3%80%81%E5%B8%82%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%8A%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（3）火力发电厂的选择" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E7%81%AB%E5%8A%9B%E5%8F%91%E7%94%B5%E5%8E%82%E7%9A%84%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="主要考虑水源、运输专用线、地质、水文、贮灰场、环保条件及靠近负荷中心。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E8%BF%90%E8%BE%93%E4%B8%93%E7%94%A8%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E3%80%81%E6%B0%B4%E6%96%87%E3%80%81%E8%B4%AE%E7%81%B0%E5%9C%BA%E3%80%81%E7%8E%AF%E4%BF%9D%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8A%E9%9D%A0%E8%BF%91%E8%B4%9F%E8%8D%B7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（4）变电所的常见类型" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%884%EF%BC%89%E5%8F%98%E7%94%B5%E6%89%80%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="变电所有屋外式、屋内式、地下式、移动式。变电所合理的供电半径见表6-7。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%98%E7%94%B5%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%B1%8B%E5%A4%96%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E5%B1%8B%E5%86%85%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%E5%8F%98%E7%94%B5%E6%89%80%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9B%E7%94%B5%E5%8D%8A%E5%BE%84%E8%A7%81%E8%A1%A86-7%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（5）高压走廊宽度应大于杆高的两倍。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%885%EF%BC%89%E9%AB%98%E5%8E%8B%E8%B5%B0%E5%BB%8A%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%E5%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E%E6%9D%86%E9%AB%98%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E5%80%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（6）电力系统与通信电路接近时，对通信线路产生静电和电磁感应，电力系统距电台、机场导航等均应有足够距离（表6-8）。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%886%EF%BC%89%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%8E%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E9%80%9A%E4%BF%A1%E7%BA%BF%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%A7%E7%94%9F%E9%9D%99%E7%94%B5%E5%92%8C%E7%94%B5%E7%A3%81%E6%84%9F%E5%BA%94%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%B7%9D%E7%94%B5%E5%8F%B0%E3%80%81%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%BA%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA%E7%AD%89%E5%9D%87%E5%BA%94%E6%9C%89%E8%B6%B3%E5%A4%9F%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%EF%BC%88%E8%A1%A86-8%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="变电所合理的供电半径   表6-7" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%8F%98%E7%94%B5%E6%89%80%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E4%BE%9B%E7%94%B5%E5%8D%8A%E5%BE%84%20%20%20%E8%A1%A86-7%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="干扰源与天线尖端最小距离   表6-8" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%B9%B2%E6%89%B0%E6%BA%90%E4%B8%8E%E5%A4%A9%E7%BA%BF%E5%B0%96%E7%AB%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8F%E8%B7%9D%E7%A6%BB%20%20%20%E8%A1%A86-8%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="（四）城市供热系统规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E5%9B%9B%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="城市采暖有分散和集中两种供热方式。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%87%87%E6%9A%96%E6%9C%89%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
      <outline text="分散式小锅炉房供热，耗煤多，有污染，逐步淘汰。分散式电供热，清洁热源是发展方向；" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%B0%8F%E9%94%85%E7%82%89%E6%88%BF%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%97%E7%85%A4%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%90%E6%AD%A5%E6%B7%98%E6%B1%B0%E3%80%82%E5%88%86%E6%95%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%94%B5%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%EF%BC%8C%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E7%83%AD%E6%BA%90%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%EF%BC%9B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
      <outline text="集中供热有热电厂供热和区域锅炉房供热两种方式，这是城市现代化的要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E6%9C%89%E7%83%AD%E7%94%B5%E5%8E%82%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E5%92%8C%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E9%94%85%E7%82%89%E6%88%BF%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    </outline>
    <outline text="供热系统是由热源、管网和热用户散热器三部分组成。供热载体分水载热体和蒸汽载热体两种。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%98%AF%E7%94%B1%E7%83%AD%E6%BA%90%E3%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%BD%91%E5%92%8C%E7%83%AD%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%95%A3%E7%83%AD%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%89%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90%E3%80%82%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E8%BD%BD%E4%BD%93%E5%88%86%E6%B0%B4%E8%BD%BD%E7%83%AD%E4%BD%93%E5%92%8C%E8%92%B8%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%BD%E7%83%AD%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%A4%E7%A7%8D%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="供热管网一般为地下敷设，在不影响市容时可架空供热管网。其管网空间位置，应满足交通及其他各种管线的间距要求。" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E7%AE%A1%E7%BD%91%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%B8%BA%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%95%B7%E8%AE%BE%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%AE%B9%E6%97%B6%E5%8F%AF%E6%9E%B6%E7%A9%BA%E4%BE%9B%E7%83%AD%E7%AE%A1%E7%BD%91%E3%80%82%E5%85%B6%E7%AE%A1%E7%BD%91%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%BA%94%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%AE%A1%E7%BA%BF%E7%9A%84%E9%97%B4%E8%B7%9D%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（五）城市燃气系统规划" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%87%83%E6%B0%94%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note="">
