    <outline text="（五）《中华人民共和国环境保护法》（以下简称《环境保护法》）（六）《中华人民共和国文物保护法》（以下简称《文物保护法》）" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%94%EF%BC%89%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%AE%80%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%8A%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%88%E5%85%AD%EF%BC%89%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E7%AE%80%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%8A%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%89%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（七）城市紫线、黄线、蓝线、绿线管理办法（1）《城市紫线管理办法》（2）《城市绿线管理办法》" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%83%EF%BC%89%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%B4%AB%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%81%E9%BB%84%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%81%E8%93%9D%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%81%E7%BB%BF%E7%BA%BF%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%B4%AB%E7%BA%BF%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%882%EF%BC%89%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E7%BA%BF%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8B%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
    <outline text="（3）《城市绿线划定技术规范》GB/T51163-2016" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%EF%BC%883%EF%BC%89%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%BB%BF%E7%BA%BF%E5%88%92%E5%AE%9A%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E3%80%8BGB/T51163-2016%3C/span%3E" _note="" _mubu_note=""/>
